%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-doctor-shahana-suicide-her-wedding-cancelled-over-bmw-gold-demand-kerala-doctor-dies-by-suicide-4641245%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-doctor-shahana-suicide-her-wedding-cancelled-over-bmw-gold-demand-kerala-doctor-dies-by-suicide-4641245%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkerala-news%2Fkerala-doctor-shahana-suicide-her-wedding-cancelled-over-bmw-gold-demand-kerala-doctor-dies-by-suicide-4641245%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Only%20Way%20to%20Deal%20With%20the%20Stubble%20Burning%20Issue%20Is%20to%20Treat%20It%20as%20a%20Policy%20Matter%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F14145605%2F6314806215_7aa3972351_b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20November%20arrives%2C%20we%20suddenly%20become%20aware%20of%20the%20hazardous%20practice%20of%20stubble%20burning%20as%20the%20air%20quality%20index%20(AQI)%20of%20Delhi%20shoots%20to%20dangerous%20levels%20of%20300%20to%20400.%20We%20worry%20about%20severe%20or%20hazardous%20pollution%20only%20when%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20breathe%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20government%20comes%20forth%20with%20its%20knee-jerk%20reaction%2C%20its%20typical%20way%20of%20dealing%20with%20any%20persistent%20problem.%20Close%20the%20schools%3B%20apply%20odd-even%20car%20driving%20on%20alternate%20days%3B%20stop%20construction%20activity%20on%20and%20off%2C%20etc.%20One%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20the%20high%20AQI%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fat-3230-punjab-records-maximum-farm-fires-in-a-day-air-quality-severe-in-parts-of-haryana%2Farticleshow%2F104990953.cms%5C%22%3Eburning%20of%20stubble%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20prefers%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20it%2C%20though%20the%20same%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20heads%20the%20government%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20city%20slicks%20know%20this%20much%20about%20rural%20India%20that%20after%20harvesting%20and%20cutting%20paddy%2C%20the%20farmer%20burns%20the%20remaining%20stubble.%20They%20can%E2%80%99t%20always%20fathom%20why.%20A%20bewildered%20city%20boy%20said%20to%20me%2C%20stubble%20has%20been%20there%20for%20centuries%2C%20why%20do%20farmers%20burn%20it%20now%3F%20Dear%20innocent%2C%20the%20practice%20started%20when%20mechanised%20cutting%20replaced%20manual%20cutting%20of%20paddy%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20advent%20of%20green%20revolution.%20With%20mechanised%20cutting%2C%20the%20stubble%20is%20cut%20so%20fine%20that%20it%20does%20not%20retain%20the%20juice%20or%20the%20texture%20to%20be%20suitable%20for%20fodder%2C%20as%20was%20the%20case%20with%20manual%20cutting.%20No%20longer%20of%20any%20use%20to%20the%20farmer%2C%20he%20burns%20the%20stubble%20to%20free%20the%20field%20for%20other%20uses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20solution%2C%20and%20indeed%20a%20productive%20one%2C%20is%20to%20turn%20the%20stubble%20into%20manure.%20One%20available%20solution%20now%20is%20to%20add%20the%20IARI-developed%20Pusa%20bio%20dispenser%20to%20the%20hard%20stubble.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20fungi-based%20liquid%20solution%20with%20the%20proclivity%20to%20soften%20it%20so%20that%20the%20resultant%20mix%20can%20be%20spread%20on%20the%20soil%20as%20manure.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20we%20expect%20the%20farmers%20to%20buy%20the%20capsules.%20They%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20incur%20the%20expense%2C%20or%20undertake%20the%20laborious%20process%20of%20mixing%20it%20with%20the%20soil.%20They%20are%20not%20convinced%20of%20its%20efficacy%20or%20its%20cost-effectiveness.%20Random%20media%20promotion%20and%20government%20prodding%20have%20failed%20to%20motivate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20routinely%20resorts%20to%20banning%20stubble%20burning.%20We%20know%20that%20legal%20bans%20are%20ineffective%20in%20our%20corruption-prone%20society.%20All%20that%20happens%20is%20that%20the%20authority%20in%20charge%20makes%20money%20from%20bribes%20while%20the%20law%20is%20trashed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20the%20only%20way%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20burning%20issue%20is%20to%20treat%20it%20as%20a%20policy%20matter%2C%20similar%20to%20building%20roads%20and%20bridges%20or%20policing%20and%20defence.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20price%20is%20paid%20by%20the%20general%20public%20through%20compromised%20health%20and%20productivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20needs%20to%20be%20addressed%20through%20a%20multi-pronged%20and%20well-planned%20policy.%20One%20potential%20solution%20could%20involve%20purchasing%20stubble%20from%20farmers%20and%20storing%20it%20at%20nearby%20manned%20centres.%20The%20establishment%20of%20numerous%20collection%20and%20storage%20centres%20in%20close%20proximity%20to%20farms%20would%20be%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETechnologies%20such%20as%20the%20Pusa%20dispenser%20or%20any%20new%20materials%20resulting%20from%20future%20research%20could%20then%20be%20employed%20to%20convert%20the%20stubble%20into%20manure.%20The%20final%20product%20could%20be%20sold%20back%20to%20farmers%20at%20a%20minimal%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20too%20much%20to%20ask%20for.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20government%20manages%20many%20projects%20dispersed%20over%20vast%20areas%2C%20such%20as%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStubble%20management%20would%20be%20less%20widespread%20as%20it%20would%20cover%20only%20two%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20we%20hope%20this%20would%20happen%20in%20the%20near%20future!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMridula%20Garg%20is%20a%20Hindi%20writer%20and%20Sahitya%20Akademi%20award%20winner.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701930630000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F12%2F14145605%2F6314806215_7aa3972351_b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-only-way-to-deal-with-the-stubble-burning-issue-is-to-treat-it-as-a-policy-matter%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20potential%20solution%20could%20involve%20purchasing%20stubble%20from%20farmers%20and%20storing%20it%20at%20nearby%20manned%20centres.%20Technologies%20such%20as%20the%20Pusa%20dispenser%20could%20be%20used%20to%20convert%20the%20stubble%20into%20manure.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-only-way-to-deal-with-the-stubble-burning-issue-is-to-treat-it-as-a-policy-matter%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Probe%20Agency%20Files%20Chargesheet%20Against%20Vivo%20In%20Money%20Laundering%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20filed%20its%20first%20charge%20sheet%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20money%20laundering%20probe%20against%20Chinese%20smartphone%20maker%20vivo%20and%20some%20others%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prosecution%20complaint%20has%20been%20filed%20before%20a%20special%20court%20here%20on%20Wednesday%20under%20the%20criminal%20sections%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20and%20Vivo-India%20has%20been%20named%20an%20accused%20apart%20from%20those%20arrested%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20sources%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20probe%20agency%20arrested%20four%20persons%2C%20including%20the%20MD%20of%20the%20Lava%20International%20mobile%20company%20Hari%20Om%20Rai%2C%20in%20this%20investigation.%20The%20others%20who%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20were%20Chinese%20national%20Guangwen%20alias%20Andrew%20Kuang%2C%20Chartered%20Accountants%20Nitin%20Garg%20and%20Rajan%20Malik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20then%20claimed%20in%20its%20remand%20papers%20before%20a%20local%20court%20here%20that%20the%20alleged%20activities%20of%20the%20four%20enabled%20Vivo-India%20to%20make%20wrongful%20gains%20that%20were%20detrimental%20to%20the%20economic%20sovereignty%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20raided%20vivo-India%20and%20its%20linked%20persons%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20claiming%20to%20have%20busted%20a%20major%20money%20laundering%20racket%20involving%20Chinese%20nationals%20and%20multiple%20Indian%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20then%20alleged%20that%20a%20whopping%20Rs%2062%2C476%20crore%20was%20%26quot%3Billegally%26quot%3B%20transferred%20by%20Vivo-India%20to%20China%20to%20avoid%20payment%20of%20taxes%20in%20India.%20The%20company%20had%20said%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bfirmly%20adheres%20to%20its%20ethical%20principles%20and%20remains%20dedicated%20to%20legal%20compliance.%26quot%3B%20Rai%20had%20recently%20told%20a%20court%20here%20that%20though%20his%20company%20and%20Vivo-India%20were%20in%20talks%20to%20launch%20a%20joint%20venture%20in%20India%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20he%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20Chinese%20firm%20or%20its%20representatives%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20not%20derived%20any%20monetary%20benefit%2C%20nor%20has%20he%20engaged%20in%20any%20transaction%20with%20Vivo%20or%20any%20entity%20allegedly%20related%20to%20Vivo%2C%20let%20alone%20having%20been%20associated%20with%20any%20alleged%20'proceeds%20of%20crime'%2C%26quot%3B%20Rai's%20lawyer%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20filed%20an%20enforcement%20case%20information%20report%20(ECIR)%2C%20the%20ED%20equivalent%20of%20a%20police%20FIR%2C%20on%20February%203%20after%20studying%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20FIR%20of%20December%20last%20year%20against%20an%20associated%20company%20of%20vivo%2C%20Grand%20Prospect%20International%20Communication%20Pvt%20Ltd%20(GPICPL)%2C%20its%20directors%2C%20shareholders%20and%20some%20others%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20complaint%20was%20filed%20by%20the%20Corporate%20Affairs%20Ministry%20alleging%20that%20GPICPL%20and%20its%20shareholders%20used%20%26quot%3Bforged%26quot%3B%20identification%20documents%20and%20%26quot%3Bfalsified%26quot%3B%20addresses%20at%20the%20time%20of%20incorporation%20of%20the%20company%20in%20December%202014.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701930480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Ffq6o12rs_vivo-logo-reuters_625x300_13_July_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-vivo-money-laundering-case-chargesheet-filed-by-enforcement-directorate-4641436%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20filed%20its%20first%20charge%20sheet%20in%20connection%20with%20its%20money%20laundering%20probe%20against%20Chinese%20smartphone%20maker%20vivo%20and%20some%20others%2C%20official%20sources%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-vivo-money-laundering-case-chargesheet-filed-by-enforcement-directorate-4641436%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-vivo-money-laundering-case-chargesheet-filed-by-enforcement-directorate-4641436%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchinese-smartphone-maker-vivo-money-laundering-case-chargesheet-filed-by-enforcement-directorate-4641436%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fidel%20and%20Raul%20Castro's%20sister%2C%20who%20fled%20Cuba%20and%20worked%20with%20CIA%2C%20dies%20aged%2090%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701930180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2