0wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%2015-member%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20an%20outcome%20must%20be%20avoided%20at%20all%20costs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuterres%20invoked%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%20he%20took%20office%20in%202017%2C%20Article%2099%20of%20the%20UN%20Charter.%20This%20states%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Secretary-General%20may%20bring%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20any%20matter%20which%20in%20his%20opinion%20may%20threaten%20the%20maintenance%20of%20international%20peace%20and%20security.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20focused%20in%20particular%20on%20the%20difficulties%20in%20delivering%20aid%20and%20providing%20health%20care%20to%20people%20in%20the%20enclave.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20current%20conditions%20are%20making%20it%20impossible%20for%20meaningful%20humanitarian%20operations%20to%20be%20conducted%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnowhere%20is%20safe%20in%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20pushed%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20humanitarian%20cease-fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20a%20humanitarian%20cease-fire%2C%20the%20means%20of%20survival%20can%20be%20restored%2C%20and%20humanitarian%20assistance%20can%20be%20delivered%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20timely%20manner%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Security%20Council%2C%20currently%20chaired%20by%20Ecuador%2C%20has%20held%20several%20sessions%20on%20the%20conflict%20in%20Gaza%20since%20Hamas%20group%E2%80%99s%20October%207%20attacks%20in%20Israel%20that%20killed%201%2C200%20people%20with%20240%20more%20taken%20hostage.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20offensive%20in%20Gaza%20has%20since%20killed%20more%20than%2013%20times%20that%20number%20of%20Palestinians%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fhow-many-palestinians-have-died-gaza-war-how-will-counting-continue-2023-12-06%2F%5C%22%3E16%2C015%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20direct%20bombings%20and%20violence%2C%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20also%20facing%20an%20acute%20humanitarian%20crisis%2C%20with%20a%20shortage%20of%20food%2C%20water%20and%20basic%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20the%20US%20and%20UK%20both%20permanent%20members%20with%20veto%20rights%20and%20a%20typically%20supportive%20stance%20towards%20Israel%2C%20the%20body%20has%20struggled%20to%20agree%20on%20very%20far-reaching%20statements%20or%20appeals%20about%20the%20conflict%20%E2%80%93%20not%20even%20a%20call%20for%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%2C%20after%20four%20draft%20texts%20were%20rejected%2C%20the%20Security%20Council%20did%20issue%20an%20appeal%20for%20%E2%80%9Cextended%20humanitarian%20pauses%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fun-chief-rings-alarm-bell-global-security-threat-gaza-war-2023-12-06%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20has%20given%20the%20security%20council%20a%20brief%20draft%20resolution%20that%20would%20act%20on%20Guterres%E2%80%99%20letter%20by%20demanding%20an%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire%E2%80%9D.%20The%20UAE%20reportedly%20aims%20to%20put%20the%20text%20to%20a%20vote%20on%20Friday%2C%20when%20the%20council%20is%20due%20to%20be%20briefed%20by%20Guterres%20on%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20DW.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701924858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07102341%2FGAruRAMWYAA72WK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-chief-invokes-little-used-un-charter-article-to-demands-ceasefire-in-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20are%20facing%20a%20severe%20risk%20of%20collapse%20of%20the%20humanitarian%20system.%20The%20situation%20is%20fast%20deteriorating%20into%20a%20catastrophe%20with%20potentially%20irreversible%20implications%20for%20Palestinians%20as%20a%20whole%20and%20for%20peace%20and%20security%20in%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20Guterres%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%2015-member%20Security%20Council.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fun-chief-invokes-little-used-un-charter-article-to-demands-ceasefire-in-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vicky%20on%20FIRST%20meeting%20with%20Kat's%20family%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701924542000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105800518%2Cimgsize-43590.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-says-katrina-kaifs-family-saw-him-dancing-on-tip-tip-barsa-paani-in-the-first-meeting-the-ice-was-broken-%2Farticleshow%2F105800531.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105800531.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%20and%20Katrina%20Kaif%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%20December%202021.%20Vicky%20revealed%20that%20he%20met%20Katrina's%20family%20for%20the%20first%20time%20just%20one%20week%20before%20they%20got%20married%2C%20here's%20what%20happened%20then...%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fvicky-kaushal-says-katrina-kaifs-family-saw-him-dancing-on-tip-tip-barsa-paani-in-the-first-meeting-the-ice-was-broken-%2Farticleshow%2F105800531.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Boy%20Dies%20After%20Eating%20Poisonous%20Berries%20On%20A%20Park%20Stroll%20With%20His%20Father%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2014-year-old%20boy%20died%20after%20eating%20poisonous%20berries%20he%20found%20during%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20park%20with%20his%20father%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fhome-news%2Fschoolboy-dies-poisonus-berries-manchester-b2457894.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Independent%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ereported.%20The%20boy%20named%20Benn%20Curran-Nicholls%20had%20severe%20autism%20with%20intellectual%20impairment%20used%20to%20regularly%20take%20morning%20walks%20through%20a%20local%20park%20for%20exercise.%20He%20stopped%20at%20a%20yew%20tree%20he%20frequently%20liked%20to%20climb.%20The%20teen%20reportedly%20ate%20some%20yew%20tree%20berries%20and%20leaves%2C%20as%20neither%20he%20nor%20his%20father%20knew%20they%20were%20poisonous.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBenn%20and%20his%20father%2C%20went%20for%20a%20walk%20in%20the%20park%20on%20September%2018%2C%20last%20year.%20Later%20that%20day%2C%20at%206%20pm%2C%20the%20teenager%20became%20unwell%20and%20suddenly%20collapsed.%20He%20was%20rushed%20to%20the%20Royal%20Manchester%20Children's%20Hospital%20by%20emergency%20ambulance%20where%20he%20died%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20September%2019%2C%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToxilogy%20report%20revealed%20that%20he%20died%20of%20%26quot%3Brefractory%20cardiogenic%20shock%20due%20to%20taxane%20alkaloid%20poisoning%26quot%3B%20from%20ingesting%20the%20berries%20and%20leaves.%20The%20report%20further%20said%20that%20although%20yew%20trees%20poisonings%20are%20rare%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bnumber%20of%20cases%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssistant%20Coroner%20for%20Manchester%20City%20Council%2C%20Andrew%20Bridgman%2C%20expressed%20apprehensions%20regarding%20the%20authorities'%20management%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20their%20choice%20not%20to%20issue%20a%20public%20alert%20regarding%20the%20hazards%20associated%20with%20yew%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20extensive%20discussion%2C%20the%20council%20and%20the%20UK%20Health%20Security%20Agency%20(UKHSA)%20opted%20against%20issuing%20an%20alert%20due%20to%20concerns%20that%20it%20might%20pose%20a%20greater%20risk%20of%20causing%20harm%20than%20providing%20benefit%2C%20given%20the%20relatively%20infrequent%20occurrence%20of%20deaths%20from%20yew%20tree%20poisoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20email%20from%20UKHSA%20to%20the%20council%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20agreed%20at%20present%20that%20there%20was%20probably%20a%20risk%20of%20doing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%20from%20any%20comms%20put%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BW%20would%20be%20very%20concerned%20about%20unintended%20consequences%20from%20comms%20messages%2C%20e.g.%20highlighting%20the%20risk%20of%20harm%20which%20may%20in%20turn%20provide%20a%20source%20for%20people%20to%20self-harm%20as%20a%20potential%20route%20for%20suicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20coroner%20described%20the%20decision%20as%20%26quot%3Billogical.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBerries%20and%20the%20like%20might%20be%20attractive%20to%20young%20children%20who%20would%20not%20recognise%20the%20dangers%20and%20risks%2C%20of%20even%20illness%20let%20alone%20death%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20preventing%20future%20deaths%20report.%20%26quot%3BThe%20poisonous%20nature%20of%20the%20yew%20tree%20is%20not%2C%20on%20the%20evidence%2C%20well%20known%20to%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20appears%20to%20be%20focused%20on%20comms%20solely%20about%20the%20yew%20tree%20and%20the%20risks%20of%20identifying%20an%20additional%20means%20of%20deliberate%20ingestion%20for%20suicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20consideration%20was%20given%20to%20highlighting%20the%20risks%20of%20eating%20wild%20berries%20and%2For%20leaves%20in%20more%20general%20terms.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20circumstance%20it%20is%20my%20view%20that%20the%20decision%20not%20to%20put%20out%20public%20health%20messages%2C%20either%20specific%20to%20the%20yew%20tree%20or%20in%20more%20general%20terms%2C%20was%20not%20properly%20and%20fully%20thought%20through.%20It%20should%20be%20re-visited.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Bridgman%20concluded%20that%20there%20existed%20a%20potential%20for%20a%20fatality%20under%20comparable%20circumstances%20and%20that%20disseminating%20information%20to%20the%20public%20regarding%20the%20hazards%20of%20yew%20trees%20would%20mitigate%20this%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20opinion%20action%2C%20namely%20further%20consideration%2C%20should%20be%20taken%20to%20prevent%20future%20deaths%20and%20I%20believe%20you%20have%20the%20power%20to%20take%20such%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Manchester%20City%20Council%20spokesperson%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20thoughts%20are%20with%20the%20family%20in%20this%20heartbreaking%20case.%20It's%20a%20matter%20which%20we%20are%20taking%20extremely%20seriously%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20take%20advice%20on%20best%20practice%20and%20respond%20to%20the%20coroner's%20recommendations%20in%20due%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20UKHSA%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20thoughts%20remain%20with%20the%20family.%20UKHSA%20continues%20to%20support%20colleagues%20at%20Manchester%20City%20Council%20regarding%20this%20tragic%20case%20and%20we%20will%20respond%20to%20the%20coroner's%20recommendations%20in%20due%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701924360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2F4cudn5qo_berries-generic_625x300_07_December_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fboy-14-collapses-and-dies-after-eating-poisonous-berries-on-a-park-stroll-with-his-father-in-uk-4641212%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20teen%20reportedly%20ate%20some%20yew%20tree%20berries%20and%20leaves