t%20aims%20to%20amend%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reorganisation%20Act%2C%202019%2C%20and%20The%20Jammu%20%26amp%3B%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023%2C%20aimed%20at%20amending%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Reservation%20Act%2C%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20legislations%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20tweak%20the%20political%20landscape%20to%20its%20advantage%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20by%20wooing%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20and%20Pahadia%20community%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20Bill%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20there%20were%2037%20seats%20in%20Jammu%20which%20have%20now%20become%2043%2C%20earlier%20there%20were%2046%20seats%20in%20Kashmir%20which%20have%20now%20become%2047%2C%20and%2024%20seats%20have%20been%20kept%20reserved%20for%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20because%20POK%20is%20ours%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said%2C%20reiterating%20a%20position%20India%20has%20held%20historically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legislative%20assembly%20initially%20had%20100%20members%20including%2024%20for%20PoK%2C%20up%20to%201988%20when%20the%20seats%20were%20increased%20to%20111.%20The%2024%20seats%20are%20however%20not%20taken%20into%20consideration%20during%20the%20quorum%20calculation%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20total%20contestable%20seats%20were%2087%20including%20four%20for%20Ladakh.%20After%20delimitation%20in%202020%2C%20the%20total%20number%20of%20seats%20rose%20to%20114%2C%20which%20included%20the%20seats%20for%20PoK.%20But%20it%20is%20the%20number%20of%20nominated%20seats%20that%20has%20raised%20eyebrows.%20It%20is%20believed%20that%20these%20members%20will%20mainly%20be%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20from%20the%20Valley%2C%20tilting%20the%20balance%20away%20from%20a%20Muslim-majority%20Valley.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20there%20were%20107%20seats%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20assembly%2C%20now%20there%20are%20114%20seats%2C%20earlier%20there%20were%20two%20nominated%20members%20in%20the%20assembly%2C%20now%20there%20will%20be%20five%2C%E2%80%9D%20Shah%20said.%20The%20state%20governor%20has%20the%20power%20to%20nominate%20these%20members%20of%20which%20two%20will%20be%20women%2C%20one%20a%20Kashmiri%20migrant%20and%20one%20from%20PoK%2C%20Shah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtests%20had%20broken%20out%20especially%20in%20the%20Valley%20when%20the%20draft%20of%20the%20delimitation%20report%20was%20submitted%2C%20because%20it%20was%20felt%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fheres-why-neither-kashmir-nor-jammu-is-happy-with-delimitation-commissions-draft-report%5C%22%3Ecriterion%20of%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20ignored.%20Kashmir%20accounted%20for%2056%25%20of%20the%20population%20per%20the%202011%20census%20which%20formed%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20delimitation%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20subverting%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20people%20by%20controlling%20the%20levers%20from%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%2C%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Majlis-E-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20reserve%20seats%20for%20Pandits%20%E2%80%93%20name%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%20He%20also%20said%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%9Cdisplaced%20persons%E2%80%9D%20does%20not%20include%20Muslims%20who%20%E2%80%9Cin%201989%2C%20when%20the%20Army%20went%20into%20their%20areas%20in%20Keran%2C%20Karna%2C%20Poonch%2C%20Rajouri%2C%20several%20villagers%20were%20forced%20to%20migrate%20to%20PoK.%20Of%20these%203%25%20are%20Muslims%2C%20the%20rest%20are%20Pahadias%20and%20Gujjars%20and%20yet%20there%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20them%20in%20the%20Bill.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20in%20his%20reply%20to%20the%20House%2C%20Shah%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20mention%20Aksai%20Chin%20in%20the%20same%20breath%20as%20PoK.%C2%A0On%20August%205%2C%202019%20though%2C%20while%20reading%20down%20Article%20370%2C%20Shah%20had%20thundered%20that%20Aksai%20Chin%20is%20Indian%20territory.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20make%20it%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20every%20single%20time%20we%20say%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20it%20includes%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir%20(including%20Gilgit-Baltistan)%20as%20well%20as%20Aksai%20Chin.%20Let%20there%20be%20no%20doubt%20over%20it.%20Entire%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%2C%20India%20has%20reportedly%20lost%20over%201%2C000%20square%20km%20of%20land%20to%20Chinese%20occupation.%20While%20Aksai%20Chin%20is%20part%20of%20the%20union%20territory%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20no%20seats%20have%20been%20reserved%20in%20the%20assembly%20from%20here%20traditionally%2C%20an%20anomaly%20that%20was%20not%20corrected%20either%20in%20the%20delimitation%20exercise%20or%20the%20state%20reorganisation%20Bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmiri%20Pandits%20apart%2C%20the%20Bill%20is%20being%20seen%20at%20targeting%20the%20Muslim-majority%20Pahadia%20community%20that%20inhabits%20primarily%20the%20hilly%20and%20border%20areas%20of%20the%20state%2C%20and%20whom%20the%20BJP%20sees%20as%20a%20promising%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Pahadias%20be%20classified%20as%20OBCs%20was%20based%20on%20a%20recommendation%20of%20the%20G.D.%20Sharma%20Commission%20constituted%20in%20March%202020%20to%20review%20reservations%20for%20different%20categories.%20The%20Commission%20had%20recommended%20the%20classification%20of%20new%20groups%20as%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20and%20Scheduled%20Castes%2C%20and%20rechristening%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Csocial%20castes%E2%80%9D%20category%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20%E2%80%9Cother%20backward%20classes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pahadias%20have%20been%20given%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20status%2C%20and%20nine%20seats%20under%20the%20new%20Act%20have%20been%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribes.%20That%20is%20not%20all.%20The%20Act%20seeks%20to%20change%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20a%20section%20of%20people%20who%20were%20earlier%20described%20as%20%E2%80%9Cweak%20and%20under%20privileged%20classes%20(social%20castes)%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cother%20backward%20classes%E2%80%9D%20so%20they%20can%20seek%20quotas%20in%20appointments%20and%20admissions.%20Significantly%2C%20the%20Pahadias%20will%20get%204%25%20quota%20in%20jobs%20under%20their%20new%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20claims%20by%20the%20home%20minister%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20brought%20lasting%20peace%20to%20the%20region%20and%20was%20committed%20towards%20its%20development%2C%20National%20Conference%20president%20Farooq%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CDuring%20the%20G20%20meeting%20that%20you%20held%20in%20the%20state%2C%20you%20said%20it%20was%20a%20great%20meeting.%20What%20tourism%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20Kashmir%3F%20What%20development%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20Kashmir%3F%20You%20could%20not%20take%20the%20members%20of%20G20%20to%20Gulmarg%2C%20you%20could%20not%20take%20them%20to%20Kulgam%2C%20you%20could%20not%20take%20them%20to%20Dachigam.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20impassioned%20speech%20during%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20motion%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAs%20chief%20minister%20I%20tried%20to%20bring%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20back%20home.%20When%20we%20tried%2C%20inimical%20forces%20from%20across%20the%20border%20killed%20innocent%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20in%20a%20village%20near%20Ganderbal.%20Immediately%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20the%20vehicles%20to%20bring%20them%20back%20home.%20I%20want%20to%20ask%20you%2C%20in%20your%2010%20years%2C%20how%20many%20have%20you%20brought%20back%20home%3F%20None.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutside%20the%20House%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Amit%20Shah%20accusing%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20prime%20minister%2C%20of%20blundering%20on%20Kashmir%2C%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20don%E2%80%99t%20share%20the%20complete%20facts.%20For%20instance%20they%20say%20our%20forces%20could%20have%20marched%20to%20Muzaffarabad%20in%20Pakistan.%20The%20truth%20is%20in%20order%20to%20save%20Poonch%20and%20Rajouri%2C%20the%20Army%20had%20to%20be%20diverted%20there.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20reason%20these%20areas%20are%20a%20part%20of%20India%20today%20or%20these%20too%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20why%20India%20had%20to%20take%20the%20Kashmir%20issue%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20Abdullah%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20no%20other%20way%20in%20those%20circumstances%20then.%20Lord%20Mountbatten%20and%20others%20advised%20accordingly%20and%20even%20Sardar%20(Vallabhai)%20Patel%20agreed%20that%20we%20need%20to%20go%20to%20the%20United%20Nation.%20Now%20these%20people%20are%20misleading%20the%20people.%20What%20can%20one%20do.%20But%20at%20that%20point%20of%20time%2C%20there%20was%20no%20way%20out.%20The%20UNSC%20kept%20those%20who%20were%20attacked%20and%20those%20who%20attacked%20on%20the%20same%20pedestal%20instead%20of%20taking%20on%20those%20who%20attacked%20India.%20They%20did%20this%20because%20there%20was%20pressure%20from%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20US%20was%20on%20the%20side%20of%20Pakistan.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701920396000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07090841%2FGAp6IW8a0AAJZ__.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparliament-passed-two-important-laws-on-jk-heres-what-they-will-do%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20two%20legislations%20are%20being%20viewed%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20tweak%20the%20political%20landscape%20to%20its%20advantage%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20by%20wooing%20the%20Kashmiri%20Pandits%20and%20Pahadia%20community%20of%20the%20region.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C