hief%20at%20Twitter%20said%20an%20advisor%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20wanted%20make%20huge%20cuts%20in%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAlan%20Rosa%20says%20in%20a%20lawsuit%20that%20the%20advisor%20wanted%2050%25%20of%20the%20security%20budget%20cut%20%26quot%3Bby%20midnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERosa%20alleges%20that%20when%20he%20raised%20concerns%2C%20he%20was%20fired%20five%20days%20later%20in%20December%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Twitter%20head%20of%20security%20Alan%20Rosa%20is%20accusing%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20one%20of%20his%20advisors%20of%20cutting%20costs%20that%20would%20make%20the%20company%20breach%20federal%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20then%20firing%20Rosa%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs3.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F24193909%2Fgovuscourtsnjd53756110.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Musk%20and%20X%20filed%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20New%20Jersey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Rosa%20alleged%20that%20one%20of%20Musk's%20advisors%2C%20Steve%20Davis%2C%20ordered%20him%20to%20cut%20the%20company's%20physical%20security%20budget%20by%2050%25%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20or%20around%20the%20evening%20of%20December%201%2C%202022%2C%20Davis%20directed%20Plaintiff%20to%20cut%20the%20physical%20security%20budget%20by%20an%20additional%2050%25%20by%20midnight.%20This%20was%20done%20in%20hours%2C%20not%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosa's%20lawsuit%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsteve-davis-boring-company-elon-musk-career-bio-2019-11%23the-boring-companys-chief-executive-slept-at-twitters-headquarters-with-his-partner-and-newborn-baby-following-musk-taking-over-the-social-media-platform-in-late-october-the-information-reported-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavis%20is%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20Boring%20Company%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20of%20Musk's%20firms%20that%20aims%20to%20build%20tunnel%20networks%20under