show%2F105796533.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Progressives%20Need%20To%20Stop%20Hectoring%20the%20INDIA%20Parties%20on%20What%20They%20Did%20and%20Did%20Not%20Do%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20National%20Congress%20(INC)%20is%20accused%20of%20snatching%20defeat%20from%20the%20jaws%20of%20victory%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan%2C%20where%20many%20pre-election%20surveys%20suggested%20the%20party%20had%20a%20realistic%20chance%20of%20winning.%20In%20speculating%20on%20specific%20reasons%2C%20it%20has%20been%20argued%20that%20the%20INC%20did%20not%20give%20sufficient%20space%20to%20partners%20in%20the%20Indian%20National%20Development%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA).%20It%20has%20also%20been%20posited%20that%20the%20party%20did%20not%20take%20the%20issue%20of%20EVM%20tampering%2Fhacking%20seriously%20enough.%20Some%20others%20have%20argued%20that%20the%20party%20lacked%20in%20communicating%20a%20grand%20vision.%20And%20finally%2C%20some%20asserted%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20organisation%20is%20inadequate%20to%20outmanoeuvre%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E(BJP)%E2%80%99s%20organisational%20machinery%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20beset%20with%20factionalism%2C%20poor%20coordination%20between%20the%20central%20and%20state%20units%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20booth-level%20presence%2C%20did%20not%20empower%20its%20grassroots%20workers%20and%20made%20mistakes%20in%20ticket%20distribution.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20these%20reasons%20explain%20one%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20truth.%20Yet%2C%20every%20party%20(including%20the%20BJP)%20is%20afflicted%20with%20these%20problems.%20Plus%20none%20of%20these%20sufficiently%20explain%20the%20results.%20It%20is%20abundantly%20clear%20that%20progressive%20forces%20across%20India%20see%20the%20INC%20as%20the%20key%20fulcrum%20in%20any%20opposition%20against%20the%20BJP.%20That%20is%20why%20they%20legitimately%20feel%20frustrated%20that%20the%20party%20faltered.%20But%20we%20all%20need%20to%20concede%20that%20after%20a%20long%20time%2C%20it%20was%20genuinely%20in%20the%20fight.%20Nearly%20every%20pollster%2C%20analyst%2C%20journalist%20and%20conscientious%20bystander%20sincerely%20felt%20that%20the%20INC%20was%20winning%20at%20least%20three%20(and%20maybe%20even%20four)%20of%20the%20five%20state%20elections.%20Imagine%20the%20kind%20of%20organisational%20restructuring%20and%20programmatic%20recalibration%20that%20must%20have%20been%20effected%20within%20the%20INC%20for%20it%20to%20come%20so%20far.%20Although%20it%E2%80%99s%20poor%20consolation%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3Edifference%20in%20vote%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20at%20least%20four%20states%20proves%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20both%20invested%20and%20capable%20of%20a%20spirited%20fight.%20Yes%2C%20it%20can%20(and%20must)%20do%20more%20to%20redress%20internal%20faultiness%20%E2%80%93%20simply%20because%20while%20the%20BJP%20can%20afford%20to%20make%20many%20mistakes%2C%20progressive%20forces%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20to%20make%20even%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-assembly-elections-hat-trick-2024%5C%22%3EThe%20Myth%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hat-Trick%20and%20What%20the%20Statistics%20Really%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20having%20said%20that%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20that%20we%20objectively%20understand%20what%20is%20happening%2C%20so%20we%20can%20course-correct.%20After%20all%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20normal%20fight%20or%20a%20level%20playing%20field.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20the%20governing%20instruments%20of%20the%20state%20are%20being%20systematically%20deployed%20against%20the%20opposition.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%20(and%20equally%20crucially)%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20politically%20complemented%20by%20the%20Sangh%20%3Cem%3Eparivar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20360-degree%20stratagems.%20Leveraging%20films%2C%20serials%2C%20media%2C%20social%20media%2C%20books%2C%20comics%2C%20religious%20and%20cultural%20organisations%2C%20social%20organisations%20etc.%2C%20they%20consistently%20outmanoeuvre%20party%20organisations%20that%20unfortunately%20still%20limit%20themselves%20to%20elections.%20The%20bitter%20truth%20is%20that%20Indians%20perceive%20such%20electoral%20engagement%20as%20transactional%20(and%20therefore%20deal%20with%20them%20instrumentally).%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20Sangh%20focuses%20on%20building%20non-political%20relationships%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20consistently%20leverages%20for%20electoral%20purposes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProgressive%20forces%20need%20to%20understand%20that%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ethese%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20new%20frontiers%20of%20politics%20that%20they%20can%20contribute%20to.%20If%20we%20truly%20care%20about%20saving%20the%20constitutional%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20we%20need%20to%20stop%20hectoring%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20on%20what%20they%20did%20and%20did%20not%20do.%20Let%20us%20leave%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20of%20electioneering%20to%20the%20professionals.%20Progressive%20parties%20like%20the%20Congress%20are%20doing%20their%20best%2C%20with%20the%20limited%20resources%20they%20have.%20Yes%2C%20they%20can%20do%20more%20to%20remedy%20structural%20problems%20(both%20within%20and%20without).%20But%20we%20progressives%20need%20to%20desist%20from%20attributing%20these%20narrow%20losses%20to%20the%20Congress%20party%20not%20paying%20heed%20to%20our%20pet%20agendas.%20No%20matter%20how%20crucial%20that%20agenda%20may%20be%20to%20India%2C%20in%20pursuing%20such%20lines%20of%20argumentation%2C%20we%20are%20reflexively%20damaging%20the%20larger%20cause%20that%20all%20progressives%20are%20uniting%20for%20today.%20In%20this%20spirit%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20reflecting%20on%20what%20we%20can%20collectively%20do%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20rather%20than%20frittering%20away%20time%20in%20finger-pointing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20we%20need%20to%20accept%20that%20the%20goalposts%20of%20welfare%20politics%20have%20changed%20drastically.%20Even%20though%20some%20progressives%20would%20like%20to%20devote%20time%20and%20resources%20to%20forging%20inspiring%20documents%20detailing%20innovative%20policy%20ideas%20for%20party%20manifestos%2C%20these%20no%20longer%20shift%20electorates%20the%20way%20they%20once%20did.%20The%20nature%20of%20political%20consumption%20has%20changed%2C%20as%20has%20the%20nature%20of%20campaigning.%20Parties%20are%20resorting%20to%20competitive%20welfarism%20because%20that%20is%20what%20works.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20more%20parties%20offer%2C%20the%20muddier%20their%20message%20is%20perceived%20to%20be.%20So%20parties%20increasingly%20focus%20on%20a%20few%20select%20promises%20at%20the%20state%20level%2C%20and%20complement%20those%20with%20customised%20constituency-level%20promises.%20We%20can%20continue%20to%20harbour%20the%20illusion%20that%20progressive%20parties%20are%20not%20connected%20to%20the%20people%2C%20and%20keep%20proffering%20suggestions%20that%20address%20macro-level%20needs%20and%20aspirations.%20Or%20we%20can%20accept%20that%20parties%20are%20infinitely%20better%20suited%20to%20understand%20local%20issues%2C%20and%20help%20them%20connect%20with%20those%20networks%20that%20are%20even%20better%20connected%20to%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20a%20caveat%20is%20necessary%20here.%20Competitive%20welfarism%20has%20also%20become%20just%20an%20eligibility%20criterion%20to%20stay%20relevant%20in%20electoral%20races.%20Quickly%20adapting%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkarnataka-decentralised-political-process-congress-success%5C%22%3EKarnataka%20experience%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20proffers%20its%20own%20version%20of%20welfare%20schemes%20to%20nullify%20the%20propagandic%20effect%20of%20INC%E2%80%99s%20schemes.%20Consequently%2C%20promises%20(or%20delivery)%20of%20welfare%20programmes%20do%20not%20sway%20mass%20consciousness.%20To%20therefore%20focus%20exclusively%20on%20issues%20like%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eroti-kapda-makan%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esadak-bijli-paani%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ejaan-jahan-jeevika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20counterproductive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03225531%2FGAb8Es9bAAAeQQI-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687555%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20being%20greeted%20by%20party%20workers.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BJP4India%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20what%20we%20now%20need%20to%20accept%20is%20that%20today%20India%20is%20in%20an%20ideological%20era.%20Today%2C%20the%20BJP%20offers%20three%20things%20to%20the%20electorate%3A%20a)%20material%20benefits%20for%20the%20family%2Findividual%20(welfare%20schemes%20and%20promises)%3B%20b)%20enhancing%20national%20pride%20(through%20symbolic%20mega-summits%20like%20the%20G-20%2C%20alleged%20assassinations%20in%20foreign%20nations%2C%20the%20projection%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20with%20global%20leaders%20etc.)%3B%20and%20c)%20the%20promotion%2Fprotection%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHinduism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(through%20performative%20religiosity%2C%20attacks%20on%20minority%20symbols%20etc.).%20This%20heady%20combination%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindutva%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eraashtravaad%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(nationalism)%20cannot%20be%20countered%20only%20by%20welfarism.%20Nor%20can%20it%20be%20countered%20by%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbehind-congress-defeat-madhya-pradesh-kamal-nath-rejection%5C%22%3Esoft%20Hindutva%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C%2C%20which%20is%20what%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20state%20leadership%20tried%20in%20vain%20in%20two%20states.%20The%20BJP%20cannot%20be%20punched%20from%20the%20right%20because%20the%20electorate%20will%20always%20choose%20the%20original.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fheres-what-the-congress-must-do-now-to-quickly-reset-the-2024-chessboard%5C%22%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20What%20the%20Congress%20Must%20Do%20Now%20to%20Quickly%20Reset%20the%202024%20Chessboard%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20the%20Congress%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20aggressively%20project%20its%20own%20ideological%20vision%20%E2%80%93%20something%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20and%20former%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20are%20doing%20by%20unequivocally%20standing%20up%20for%20secularism%2C%20liberalism%2C%20democratic%20norms%2C%20nationalism%20and%20development.%20But%20INC%20needs%20to%20also%20breathe%20life%20into%20its%20vision%20by%20putting%20programmatic%20muscle%20behind%20it.%20What%20the%20party%20needs%20to%20do%20is%20unleash%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Freengineering-indias-consciousness%2Farticle65712443.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehundred%20ideological%20projects%20across%20the%20nation%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(which%20will%20undoubtedly%20help%20the%20entire%20INDIA%20bloc).%20And%20it%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehere%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20non-political%20progressive%20forces%20can%20make%20a%20substantive%20contribution%20to%20further%20India%E2%80%99s%20constitutional%20promise.%20These%20ideological%20projects%20are%20not%20just%20to%20reshape%20mass%20consciousness%20but%20also%20to%20forge%20fresh%20relationships%20with%20the%20people.%20The%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(BJY)%20was%20one%20such%20initiative%2C%20which%20reconnected%20progressives%20across%20India%20with%20the%20INC.%20But%20to%20be%20effective%2C%20many%20more%20projects%20will%20need%20to%20be%20spearheaded.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20example%2C%20progressives%20need%20a%20galaxy%20of%20projects%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20sub-caste%20Dalits%2C%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20and%20Adivasis%20on%20a%20socio-cultural%20level.%20The%20INDIA%20parties%20are%20undoubtedly%20beginning%20to%20re-engineer%20their%20party%20structures%20(for%20example%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fres.cloudinary.com%2Fdkplc2mbj%2Fimage%2Fupload%2Fv1695636030%2FText_Congress_Consitution_English_15_July_2023_Final_4b6c600ed6.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%20VI-A%20and%20B%20of%20the%20INC%E2%80%99s%20constitution%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20recently%20amended%20at%20its%20Raipur%20plenary%20to%20reserve%2050%25%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20%5BSCs%5D%2C%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20%5BSTs%5D%2C%20OBCs%2C%20women%2C%20and%20minorities).%20They%20are%20also%20proposing%20to%20deepen%20India%E2%80%99s%20social%20justice%20paradigm%20to%20inspire%20historically%20marginalised%20sections%20of%20society%20(most%20notably%2C%20the%20promise%20of%20the%20caste%20census).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20these%20are%20not%20nearly%20enough%2C%20given%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20not%20only%20appropriates%20SC-ST-OBC%20icons%20but%20also%20celebrates%20their%20festivals%20while%20giving%20sub-castes%20political%20representation.%20That%20is%20why%2C%20as%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fdespite-caste-survey-politics-is-obc-vote-eluding-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAxis%20My%20India%20poll%20shows%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20enjoyed%20a%2026%25-point%20lead%20among%20the%20OBCs%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20a%2024%25-point%20lead%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20a%2013%25-point%20lead%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%20The%20election-oriented%20organisations%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20need%20help%20in%20programmatically%20countering%20the%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20designs%20(which%20are%20designed%20to%20capture%20hearts%20and%20minds%20while%20injecting%20communal%2C%20casteist%2C%20illiberal%20and%20undemocratic%20values).%20This%20is%20where%20progressives%20can%20tangibly%20help.%20Instead%20of%20just%20amplifying%20their%20issues%20in%20the%20media%2Fsocial%20media%20or%20even%20in%20parliament%2C%20it%20would%20be%20infinitely%20more%20meaningful%20if%20we%20put%20boots%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20progressives%20can%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fopinion%2Flead%2Fan-open-letter-to-the-indian-film-industry%2Farticle66337866.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einsert%20liberal%2C%20secular%20and%20democratic%20values%20in%20films%20and%20serials%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(instead%20of%20limiting%20themselves%20to%20clandestinely%20suggesting%20campaign%20slogans%20and%20limericks%2C%20which%20even%20professional%20advertising%20agencies%20can%20be%20hired%20to%20do).%20Progressives%20can%20also%20work%20at%20the%20grassroots%20with%20Adivasi%20communities%20(to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EVanvasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20weaving%20away%20Adivasis%20away%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%20these%20state%20elections).%20Progressives%20can%20also%20work%20to%20mobilise%20women%20through%20constructive%20work%20and%20cultural%20programmes%20(to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDurga%20Vahini%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EMahila%20Morcha%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20which%20were%20instrumental%20in%20ensuring%20women%20became%20a%20voting%20bloc%20for%20the%20BJP).%20Likewise%2C%20civil%20society%20can%20coordinate%20within%20themselves%20to%20mobilise%20sub-district%20level%20progressives%20for%20a%20plethora%20of%20community-based%20socio-cultural%20programmes.%20Diaspora%20progressives%20can%20similarly%20mobilise%20progressives%20in%20every%20nation%2C%20both%20to%20support%20progressive%20causes%20in%20India%20and%20to%20counter%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindu%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20the%20Overseas%20Friends%20of%20BJP.%20And%20finally%2C%20instead%20of%20symbolic%20and%20theatric%20pietism%20before%20elections%2C%20it%20would%20be%20expedient%20to%20spearhead%20a%20pan-India%20initiative%20to%20reclaim%20and%20reform%20Hinduism%20by%20working%20with%20its%20more%20progressive%20stakeholders%20(temple%20trusts%2C%20societies%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eakharas%2Fmaths%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20etc.%2C%20which%20are%20simmering%20at%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%20for%20appropriating%20their%20functions).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThirdly%2C%20for%20this%20plan%20to%20succeed%2C%20all%20INDIA%20parties%20(from%20the%20national%20to%20the%20district%20level)%20need%20to%20back%20such%20ideological%20projects%20at%20the%20highest%20level.%20Of%20course%2C%20such%20ideological%20projects%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emust%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20perforce%20be%20delinked%20from%20elections%20and%20the%20party%20organisations.%20Otherwise%2C%20they%20will%20always%20be%20sacrificed%20on%20the%20altar%20of%20political%20exigencies.%20However%2C%20if%20this%20can%20be%20fructified%2C%20we%20recreate%20the%20Congress%20Movement%20(an%20INDIA-Movement%20if%20I%20may)%20that%20transcends%20partisan%20lines%20and%20gives%20an%20actual%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Etakkar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(counter)%20to%20the%20Sangh%20parivar.%20This%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ramping%20up%20last-mile%20connectivity%20(which%20is%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20an%20upper%20hand%2C%20since%20it%20is%20able%20to%20convert%20waves%20into%20votes).%20It%20will%20also%20act%20as%20a%20feedback%20mechanism%20for%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20(which%20is%20sorely%20needed%20especially%20for%20the%20national%20parties%2C%20which%20rely%20on%20state%20units%20for%20feedback.%20This%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest%2C%20given%20state%20units%20are%20averse%20to%20passing%20on%20any%20feedback%20that%20disrupts%20the%20status%20quo).%20And%20most%20importantly%2C%20like%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20it%20will%20constructively%20channelise%20every%20patriot%20in%20the%20defence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20131007%2FF1TiMrZXsAAWGmx-1024x683.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664098%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EJoint%20opposition%20parties%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40kharge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFinally%2C%20this%20requires%20progressive%20parties%20to%20both%20unlearn%20and%20relearn%20some%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirstly%2C%20they%20need%20to%20accept%20the%20limitations%20of%20creating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%2C%20mahol%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(a%20narrative%20wave)%20to%20win%20elections.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20in%20creating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20parties%20outsource%20key%20political%20functions%20to%20external%20agencies%20(crippling%20parties%20structurally%20and%20diverting%20scarce%20resources).%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20given%20its%20disproportionate%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20chokehold%20on%20the%20media%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20better%20placed%20at%20generating%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehawa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20resource-intensive%20method%20of%20campaigning%20also%20makes%20parties%20more%20susceptible%20to%20diverting%20resources%20from%20pro-people%20schemes%20when%20in%20government%20(which%20is%20what%20led%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20in%20Karnataka).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESecondly%2C%20progressive%20parties%20also%20need%20to%20stop%20relying%20on%20demagogues%20to%20enthuse%20electorates.%20Demagogues%20can%20temporarily%20enthral%2C%20but%20that%20rapture%20is%20limited%20to%20the%20length%20of%20the%20programme%20they%E2%80%99re%20speaking%20in.%20They%20do%20nothing%20to%20truly%20influence%20minds%20or%20convert%20them%20into%20votes.%20What%20the%20INDIA%20parties%20really%20need%20today%20and%20tomorrow%20is%20a%20veritable%20army%20of%20progressive%20evangelicals%2C%20who%20work%20consistently%20and%20silently%2C%20away%20from%20the%20media-glare.%20These%20evangelicals%20(and%20the%20ideological%20projects)%20they%20will%20spearhead%20are%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20silver%20bullet%20to%20outmatch%20the%20Sangh%20parivar%2C%20and%20the%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eamrit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20reclaim%20the%20hearts%20and%20minds%20of%20our%20people.%20Creating%20this%20institutionalised%20network%20of%20ideological%20projects%20will%20take%20time%20and%20effort.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20how%20long%20can%20we%20keep%20bandaging%20something%20that%20clearly%20needs%20surgery%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpushparaj-deshpande%5C%22%3EPushparaj%20Deshpande%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Samruddha%20Bharat%20Foundation%20and%20editor%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3ERethinking%20India%3Cem%3E%20series%20(Penguin).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701916254000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01145303%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-09-01-at-1.39.00-PM-1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fprogressives-stop-hectoring-india-parties%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Those%20who%20believe%20in%20the%20promise%20of%20India's%20constitution%20should%20leave%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%20of%20electioneering%20to%20the%20professionals.%20It%20is%20worth%20reflecting%20on%20what%20can%20be%20collectively%20done%20in%20the%20national%20interest%2C%20rather%20than%20fr