tle%22%3A%22To%20frame%20hubby%2C%20woman%20sends%20hoax%20bomb%20message%20to%20cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701913879000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105796176%2Cimgsize-16830.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fto-frame-husband-woman-sends-hoax-bomb-msg-to-cops%2Farticleshow%2F105796044.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TNN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fto-frame-husband-woman-sends-hoax-bomb-msg-to-cops%2Farticleshow%2F105796044.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UNLV%20shooting%3A%20Police%20say%20three%20dead%20in%20University%20of%20Nevada%20shooting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701913144000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FAE6E%2Fproduction%2F_131945644_ea24812aaa79b2c1d040c929f14f1cb96be946d3862_20_3397_19112000x1125.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67642512%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20gunman%20was%20killed%20by%20police%20after%20opening%20fire%20at%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20campus%20of%20the%20University%20of%20Nevada.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1170%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67642512%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67642512.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-67642512.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Remembering%20Yusuf%20Meherally%2C%20a%20Prominent%20Freedom%20Fighter%20Largely%20Forgotten%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06144458%2FYusufMeherallyImage.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20extraordinary%20when%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20organised%20a%20meeting%20of%20its%20party%20functionaries%20in%20Patna%20on%20November%2026%2C%20Constitution%20Day%2C%20to%20reflect%20on%20the%20Constitution%20and%20safeguard%20it%20from%20the%20alleged%20onslaught%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime%2C%20and%20also%20recall%20the%20legacy%20of%20Yusuf%20Meherally.%20A%20great%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20he%20coined%20the%20iconic%20slogans%20%E2%80%9CSimon%20Go%20Back%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9CQuit%20India%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20were%20employed%20for%20the%20freedom%20movement%20in%201928%20and%201942%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssociated%20with%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20since%201927%2C%20he%20participated%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20was%20imprisoned%20several%20times%2C%20founded%20(with%20others)%20the%20Congress%20Socialist%20Party%20(CSP)%2C%20and%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement.%20He%20also%20served%20as%20the%20first%20socialist%20Mayor%20of%20Bombay%2C%20now%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20Member%20of%20the%20Bombay%20Legislative%20Assembly.%20In%20spite%20of%20such%20a%20glorious%20legacy%2C%20Meherally%E2%80%99s%20name%20hardly%20figures%20in%20history%20textbooks%20and%20people%20in%20general%20remain%20unaware%20about%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20nine-time%20RJD%20MLA%2C%20former%20MP%20and%20minister%20in%20the%20Bihar%20government%20Vrishin%20Patel%20took%20the%20initiative%20that%20the%20party%20should%20discuss%20the%20remarkable%20legacy%20of%20Meherally%2C%20who%20was%20born%20on%20September%2023%2C%201903%20and%20breathed%20his%20last%20on%20July%202%2C%201950.%20The%20state%20president%20of%20the%20RJD%2C%20Jagadanand%20Singh%2C%20took%20it%20forward%20to%20commemorate%20the%20rich%20contributions%20of%20Meherally%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20struggle%20for%20independence%20and%20shapin%20the%20idea%20of%20India%2C%20which%20is%20now%20endangered%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20being%20invited%20to%20speak%20on%20the%20occasion%20graced%2C%20among%20others%2C%20by%20the%20youthful%20leader%20of%20RJD%20and%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMadhu%20Dandavate%E2%80%99s%20book%20%3Cem%3EYusuf%20Meherally%3A%20Quest%20for%20New%20Horizons%3C%2Fem%3E%20threw%20light%20on%20his%20address%20in%20Patna%20on%20December%2027-28%2C%201941%20to%20enlist%20the%20support%20of%20the%20people%20for%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20individual%20satyagraha%2C%20launched%20by%20him%20a%20few%20months%20before%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement%2C%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20press%20freedom.%20Among%20several%20of%20his%20satyagrahas%2C%20that%20was%20the%20only%20one%20dedicated%20to%20defend%20press%20freedom%20curbed%20by%20the%20British%20regime%20after%20India%20was%20dragged%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20its%20people.%20Meherally%20along%20with%20several%20others%20including%20Vinoba%20Bhave%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20and%20Maulana%20Azad%20participated%20in%20it.%20Gandhi%20described%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20freedom%20of%20pen%20and%20freedom%20of%20speech%20as%20foundation%20of%20Swaraj%E2%80%9D.%20He%20urged%20people%20to%20defend%20it%20with%20all%20their%20might.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20then%20flagged%20the%20point%20that%20India%20is%20now%20occupying%20the%20161st%20rank%20in%20the%20press%20freedom%20index.%20Besides%2C%20corporate%20controlled%20mainstream%20media%20is%20indulging%20in%20propaganda%20of%20the%20ruling%20regime%20at%20the%20Centre%20and%20coercive%20measures%20have%20been%20taken%20with%20impunity%20against%20several%20independent%20media%20platforms%20including%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20legacy%20of%20Meherally%20as%20an%20individual%20satyagrahi%20in%20defence%20of%20press%20freedom%20assumes%20greater%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeherally%20also%20stated%20in%20his%20Patna%20speech%20that%20the%20youth%20should%20address%20the%20rising%20communal%20problem%20by%20focusing%20attention%20on%20common%20problems%20of%20people%20regardless%20of%20their%20faiths%20and%20promote%20greater%20cultural%20fusion%20among%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20for%20establishing%20enduring%20unity%20among%20them.%20Those%20words%20sound%20so%20contemporary%20in%20present%20day-India%20for%20those%20wanting%20to%20defeat%20Hindutva%20forces%20calling%20for%20genocide%20of%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20Muslims%2C%20and%20stridently%20campaigning%20for%20their%20comprehensive%20social%20and%20economic%20boycott.%20Probably%20Meherally%2C%20as%20a%20fine%20product%20of%20our%20composite%20culture%2C%20would%20not%20have%20been%20spared%20by%20such%20forces%20on%20account%20of%20his%20faith.%20Had%20he%20been%20living%20in%20India%20now%2C%20confronting%20the%20onslaught%20of%20majoritariansim%20and%20polarisation%2C%20he%20would%20have%20been%20deeply%20anguished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20stated%20that%20Meherally%20interviewed%20Gandhi%20on%20March%2022%2C%201930%20during%20the%20historic%20Dandi%20March%20and%20asked%20how%20the%20Congress%20should%20attract%20Muslims%20to%20its%20fold%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20the%20pernicious%20propaganda%20of%20communalists.%20Gandhi%20replied%20that%20by%20serving%20Muslims%20%E2%80%93%20and%20providing%20them%20evidence%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20as%20much%20for%20them%20as%20for%20others%20%E2%80%93%20Muslims%20can%20be%20attracted%20to%20the%20party.%20He%20underlined%20that%20Dandi%20March%20centred%20around%20the%20issue%20of%20salt%2C%20and%20would%20bring%20all%20communities%20together.%20Meherally%E2%80%99s%20question%20and%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20answer%20to%20it%20constitute%20a%20remedy%20to%20save%20India%20from%20the%20grip%20of%20communal%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeherally%E2%80%99s%20vision%20that%20a%20Constituent%20Assembly%20would%20frame%20a%20Constitution%20for%20India%20flowed%20from%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20and%20now%20the%20time%20has%20come%20to%20preserve%2C%20protect%20and%20defend%20that%20vision%20which%20our%20Constitution%20embodies.%20That%20would%20be%20the%20real%20tribute%20to%20Yusuf%20Meherally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K%20R%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701912604000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06144458%2FYusufMeherallyImage.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-yusuf-meherally-a-prominent-freedom-fighter-largely-forgotten-today%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Associated%20with%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20since%201927%2C%20he%20participated%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20was%20imprisoned%20several%20times%2C%20founded%20(with%20others)%20the%20Congress%20Socialist%20Party%20(CSP)%2C%20and%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20during%20the%20Quit%20India%20movement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fremembering-yusuf-meherally-a-prominent-freedom-fighter-largely-forgotten-today%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20effectively%20tackling%20air%20pollution%20while%20India%20continues%20to%20choke%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701912490000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-12%2F07%2Ffull%2F1701911750-2597.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-effectively-tackling-air-pollution-while-india-continues-to-choke-123120700085_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20made%20strides%20in%20scrubbing%20the%20once-foul%20air%20that%20had%20become%20a%20fact%20of%20life%20each%20y