hot%20Wednesday%20and%20a%20fourth%20person%20was%20critically%20wounded%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20University%20of%20Nevada%2C%20Las%20Vegas%20campus%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20suspected%20shooter%20also%20was%20found%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20just%20before%20noon%20sent%20police%20swarming%20onto%20the%20campus%2C%20which%20is%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20miles%20from%20the%20world-famous%20Las%20Vegas%20Strip%20while%20students%20barricaded%20themselves%20in%20classrooms.%20The%20Las%20Vegas%20Metropolitan%20Police%20Department%20advised%20the%20public%20to%20%26quot%3Bavoid%20the%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20gave%20the%20all-clear%20about%2040%20minutes%20after%20the%20first%20report%20of%20an%20active%20shooter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolice%20haven't%20released%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20suspect%20or%20the%20motive%20for%20the%20attack.%20The%20shootings%20took%20place%20in%20a%20city%20still%20scarred%20by%20an%20October%202017%20attack%20by%20a%20gunman%20at%20the%20Mandalay%20Bay%20casino%20that%20killed%2060%20people%20and%20wounded%20hundreds%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdeadliest-mass-shootings-in-us-history-2017-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeadliest%20mass%20shooting%20in%20modern%20US%20history%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlerts%20went%20out%20across%20the%20campus%20after%20callers%20reported%20an%20active%20shooter%20to%20police%20at%2011%3A45%20a.m.%20Wednesday%2C%20said%20Adam%20Garcia%2C%20a%20university%20police%20official.%20He%20said%20officers%20found%20and%20%26quot%3Bengaged%26quot%3B%20a%20suspect%2C%20who%20is%20now%20dead.%20It%20was%20not%20immediately%20clear%20how%20the%20suspect%20died.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20and%20professors%20on%20the%20campus%20of%2030%2C000%20barricaded%20themselves%20inside%20classrooms%20and%20dorm%20rooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20John%20Harris%20heard%20what%20he%20later%20realized%20was%20a%20gunshot%20as%20he%20was%20getting%20out%20of%20his%20car%20in%20the%20parking%20garage%20of%20an%20on-campus%20apartment%20complex.%20In%20the%20elevator%2C%20Harris%20said%20he%20got%20an%20emergency%20text%20alert%20text%20from%20the%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20sure%20what%20to%20believe%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harris%2C%2021%2C%20who%20ended%20up%20sheltering%20at%20a%20friend's%20dorm.%20%26quot%3BBut%20as%20I%20came%20down%20to%20the%20street%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20there%20were%20a%20bunch%20of%20cops%20in%20the%20parking%20lot%20at%20the%20student%20union%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20I%20heard%20was%20a%20gunshot%20and%20this%20wasn't%20a%20drill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Kevaney%20Martin%20took%20cover%20under%20a%20desk%20in%20her%20classroom%2C%20where%20another%20faculty%20member%20and%20three%20students%20took%20shelter%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20terrifying%2C%20I%20can't%20even%20begin%20to%20explain%2C%26quot%3B%20Martin%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20trying%20to%20hold%20it%20together%20for%20my%20students%2C%20and%20trying%20not%20to%20cry%2C%20but%20the%20emotions%20are%20something%20I%20never%20want%20to%20experience%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20said%20she%20was%20texting%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones%2C%20hoping%20to%20receive%20word%20a%20suspect%20had%20been%20detained.%20When%20another%20professor%20came%20to%20the%20room%20and%20told%20everyone%20to%20evacuate%2C%20they%20joined%20dozens%20of%20others%20rushing%20out%20of%20the%20building.%20Martin%20had%20her%20students%20piled%20into%20her%20car%20and%20drove%20them%20off%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20we%20got%20away%20from%20UNLV%2C%20we%20parked%20and%20sat%20in%20silence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20said%20a%20word.%20We%20were%20in%20utter%20shock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20said%20on%20X%20that%20the%20shooter%20was%20at%20the%20Beam%20Hall%2C%20Frank%20and%20Estella%20Building%2C%20home%20of%20UNLV's%20Lee%20Business%20School%2C%20and%20that%20police%20were%20responding%20to%20an%20additional%20report%20of%20shots%20fired%20at%20the%20nearby%20student%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELas%20Vegas%20police%20posted%20on%20X%20that%20a%20suspect%20%26quot%3Bhas%20been%20located%20and%20is%20deceased%26quot%3B%20about%2040%20minutes%20after%20the%20initial%20alert%20was%20posted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20and%20the%20community%20were%20alerted%20to%20the%20emergency%20by%20a%20university%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20test%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20university%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BRUN-HIDE-FIGHT.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudent%20Matthew%20Felsenfeld%20said%20he%20and%20about%2012%20classmates%20barricaded%20their%20door%20in%20a%20building%20near%20the%20student%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20moment%20you%20call%20your%20parents%20and%20tell%20them%20you%20love%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Felsenfeld%2C%20a%2021-year-old%20journalism%20student.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20didn't%20hear%20gunfire%20or%20see%20anyone%20injured%20but%20said%20he%20saw%20out%20the%20windows%20as%20police%20staged%20to%20enter%20the%20neighboring%20building.%20a%20short%20while%20later%2C%20police%20came%20and%20ushered%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPierre%20Lescure%2C%20a%20UNLV%20senior%2C%20was%20riding%20his%20bicycle%20from%20home%20to%20campus%20for%20a%20meeting%20when%20he%20said%20about%2010%20police%20cars%20drove%20past%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20drove%20too%20fast%20and%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%2C%20just%20cops.%20It%20was%20clearly%20a%20shooting%2C%26quot%3B%20Lescure%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20could%20not%20be%20something%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUNLV's%20332-acre%20(135-hectare)%20campus%20is%20less%20than%202%20miles%20east%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20Strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20campus%20shootings%2C%20the%20Federal%20Aviation%20Administration%20issued%20a%20ground%20stop%20for%20all%20flights%20coming%20into%20Harry%20Reid%20International%20Airport.%20The%20university%20is%20roughly%202%20miles%20(3%20kilometers)%20north%20of%20the%20airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETony%20Molinaro%2C%20an%20FAA%20spokesperson%2C%20referred%20a%20request%20to%20comment%20to%20Las%20Vegas%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClasses%20were%20canceled%20at%20the%20university%2C%20and%20UNLV's%20basketball%20game%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Dayton%2C%20Ohio%2C%20was%20canceled%20Wednesday%20night%20because%20of%20the%20Las%20Vegas%20shootings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shooting%20occurred%20in%20a%20city%20still%20scarred%20by%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20mass%20killings%20in%20U.S.%20history%2C%20the%20Oct.%201%2C%202017%2C%20mass%20shooting%20at%20the%20Mandalay%20Bay%20casino%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20in%20which%2060%20were%20killed%20and%20hundreds%20more%20wounded.%20The%20UNLV%20campus%20is%20just%20over%203%20miles%20(5%20kilometers)%20from%20that%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAssociated%20Press%20reporters%20Terry%20Tang%20in%20Phoenix%20and%20Russ%20Bynum%20in%20Savannah%2C%20Georgia%2C%20contributed%20to%20this%20report.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversity-of-las-vegas-unlv-campus-shooting-victims-students-evacuate-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701912214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6571120c0ec98e92f74cfca8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversity-of-las-vegas-unlv-campus-shooting-victims-students-evacuate-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20people%20were%20fatally%20shot%20and%20a%20fourth%20person%20critically%20injured%20in%20a%20shooting%20at%20University%20of%20Nevada%2C%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20campus%2C%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20police%20said.%20The%20suspected%20shooter%20also%20was%20found%20dead