ssible%20side%20effects.%20Besides%2C%20because%20I%20write%20about%20skincare%20at%20work%2C%20I%20figured%20I%20already%20had%20the%20basics%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20after%20getting%20briefed%20on%20all%20the%20potential%20risks%20and%20the%20aftercare%20instructions%2C%20there%20were%20some%20things%20that%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20known%20before%20I%20got%20my%20first%20jab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20There's%20a%20small%20chance%20you%20can%20get%20a%20droopy%20eyelid%20%E2%80%94%20for%20weeks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20procedure%2C%20the%20nurse%20practitioner%20had%20me%20sign%20a%20form%20consenting%20to%20all%20possible%20risks%20%E2%80%94%20including%20an%20%26quot%3Beyelid%20droop%2C%26quot%3B%20also%20called%20ptosis.%20About%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.webmd.com%2Feye-health%2Feyelid-droops-after-botox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E5%25%20of%20patients%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20experience%20this%2C%20according%20to%20WebMD%2C%20with%20the%20number%20dropping%20to%201%25%20with%20more%20experienced%20dermatologists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20NP%20was%20honest%20with%20me%20that%20while%20it's%20never%20happened%20with%20one%20of%20her%20clients%2C%20some%20patients%20of%20the%20clinic%20had%20gotten%20ptosis%20in%20the%20past.%20If%20it%20were%20to%20happen%2C%20it%20would%20take%20about%203-4%20weeks%20to%20improve%20as%20the%20neurotoxin%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthree-ways-to-make-botox-last-longer-zinc-dosing-brands-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estart%20to%20wear%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20me%20worry%2C%20because%20I%20had%20a%20choir%20performance%2C%20holiday%20parties%2C%20and%20family%20events%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%20But%20I%20realized%20that%20there's%20no%20time%20in%20my%20life%20where%20I%20have%20nowhere%20to%20be%20for%20three%20weeks%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20chance%20it.%20Luckily%2C%20that%20side%20effect%20didn't%20happen%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20You%20can%20get%20headaches%2C%20but%20you%20can't%20take%20some%20common%20pain%20relievers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20not%20surprising%2C%20but%20getting%20jabbed%20with%20a%20needle%20about%2020%20times%20all%20over%20your%20forehead%20leads%20to%20mild%20discomfort.%20I%20had%20two%20tiny%20bruises%20on%20my%20forehead%20and%20a%20low-grade%20headache%20two%20days%20after%20the%20shots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20my%20NP%20warned%20me%20to%20avoid%20taking%20blood%20thinners%20like%20ibuprofen%2C%20which%20is%20what%20I%20had%20at%20home%2C%20as%20it%20could%20increase%20bruising.%20I%20ended%20up%20just%20riding%20out%20the%20headache%20because%20I%20was%20too%20lazy%20to%20buy%20Tylenol%2C%20but%20I'll%20stock%20up%20beforehand%20next%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20shouldn't%20work%20out%20or%20drink%20the%20day%20after%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20NP%20advised%20me%20not%20to%20drink%20alcohol%20or%20work%20out%20for%20at%20least%2024%20hours.%20This%20guidance%20varies%20%E2%80%94%20some%20experts%20say%20%3Cu%3Ey%3C%2Fu%3Eou%20can%20do%20moderate%20exercise%20after%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mi-skin.com%2Fblog%2Fwhen-can-i-exercise-after-botox%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20four%20hours%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Others%20say%20to%20avoid%20alcohol%20before%20the%20procedure%20and%20up%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medicalnewstoday.com%2Farticles%2Fcan-you-drink-alcohol-after-botox%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%2048%20hours%20after%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20plans%20the%20next%20day%20and%20was%20feeling%20a%20little%20burned%20out%20from%20the%20weekend%2C%20so%20it%20was%20a%20nice%20excuse%20to%20do%20nothing.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'll%20make%20sure%20to%20keep%20this%20in%20mind%20so%20I%20don't%20plan%20the%20injections%20around%20an%20event%20or