ous%20minorities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Jai%20Telangana%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20small%20coterie%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BRS%20leader%E2%80%99s%20lasting%20popularity%20among%20the%20masses%20is%20due%20to%20his%20political%20leadership%20of%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20movement.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20it%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20civil%20society%2C%20students%20of%20Osmania%20University%2C%20cultural%20groups%20and%20many%20others%20played%20just%20as%20important%20a%20role%20%E2%80%93%20if%20not%20more%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20state.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20immediately%20after%20coming%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20KCR%20sidelined%20all%20the%20other%20key%20figures%20in%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWithin%20the%20government%2C%20power%20was%20quickly%20centralised%20among%20three%20persons%3A%20KCR%2C%20his%20son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao%20(KTR)%20and%20nephew%20T.%20Harish%20Rao.%20All%20decisions%20were%20made%20from%20the%20top%2C%20while%20MLAs%20and%20other%20party%20leaders%20repeatedly%20sang%20paeans%20to%20the%20BRS%20chief.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20years%20passed%2C%20he%20was%20increasingly%20inaccessible%20not%20just%20to%20ordinary%20people%20but%20also%20to%20those%20with%20relative%20influence.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20as%20he%20was%20targeted%20by%20opposition%20parties%20for%20being%20a%20%E2%80%98farmhouse%20CM%E2%80%99%20and%20compared%20to%20feudal%20lords%20who%20lived%20in%20forts%2C%20he%20did%20not%20feel%20the%20need%20to%20be%20more%20approachable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06184107%2FKCR-KTR-Harish-1024x404.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06184107%2FKCR-KTR-Harish-1024x404.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06184107%2FKCR-KTR-Harish-300x118.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06184107%2FKCR-KTR-Harish.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-688002%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22331%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPower%20in%20the%20party%20was%20quickly%20centralised%20around%20KCR%2C%20his%20son%20KTR%20(front%2C%20second%20from%20right)%20and%20nephew%20Harish%20Rao%20(second%20from%20left).%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40BRSParty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDecision-making%20also%20seemed%20impulsive%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20outcome%20of%20consultations%20or%20democratic%20discussions.%20Take%20for%20example%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fnews%2Ftelangana-state-rtc-strike-ends-as-kcr-relents%2Farticle30108846.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eflip-flops%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20strike%20by%20employees%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Road%20Transport%20Corporation.%20Even%20his%20decision%20to%20%E2%80%98go%20national%E2%80%99%20was%20seemingly%20abandoned%20after%20the%20initial%20hype%20in%20late%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Delivery%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDuring%20his%20tenure%20as%20chief%20minister%2C%20KCR%20delivered%20a%20few%20key%20promises%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0two-thirds%20of%20voters%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Felections%2Ftelangana-assembly%2F2023-telangana-assembly-elections-brs-voted-out-despite-voters-favourable-opinion-on-governance%2Farticle67605483.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20a%20CSDS-Lokniti%20poll%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20said%20they%20were%20satisfied%20with%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20BRS%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20was%20notorious%20for%20power%20cuts%20and%20even%20the%20capital%20city%20of%20Hyderabad%20saw%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20%E2%80%9Cload%20shedding%E2%80%9D%20every%20day.%20That%20is%20decisively%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20efforts%20to%20provide%20drinking%20and%20irrigation%20water%20to%20the%20semi-arid%20region%20were%20well%20received.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20son%20and%20information%20technology%20minister%20KTR%20ensured%20that%20Hyderabad%20continues%20to%20grow%20as%20an%20industry%20hub.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20these%20reasons%2C%20he%20will%20fondly%20be%20remembered%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBook%20of%20jobs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20his%20failure%20to%20address%20key%20issues%20like%20unemployment%20and%20providing%20government%20jobs%20%E2%80%93%20a%20core%20aspect%20of%20the%20statehood%20movement%20%E2%80%93%20was%20glaring.%20His%20government%E2%80%99s%20penchant%20for%20technocracy%20was%20also%20misplaced%2C%20especially%20the%20decision%20to%20digitise%20land%20records.%20Many%20people%20claim%20that%20local%20BRS%20leaders%2C%20colluding%20with%20government%20officials%2C%20took%20possession%20of%20lands%20illegally%20by%20fudging%20the%20records.%20There%20may%20be%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fcurrent-affairs%2F251222%2Fkcrs-govt-to-face-farmers-anger-over-land-acquisition.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eat%20least%20some%20truth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20these%20allegations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20again%2C%20neither%20the%20BRS%20nor%20KCR%20made%20any%20effort%20%E2%80%93%20even%20a%20perfunctory%20promise%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation%20%E2%80%93%20to%20assuage%20people.%20Their%20repeated%20claims%20that%20the%20Dharani%20portal%20was%20foolproof%20may%20have%20assured%20others%20but%20not%20people%20who%20lost%20lands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x509.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-1024x509.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM-300x149.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F23135410%2FScreenshot-2023-10-23-at-1.45.01%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22418%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20BRS%20government%E2%80%99s%20Dharani%20portal%20has%20been%20controversial%2C%20and%20many%20people%20claim%20that%20local%20party%20leaders%2C%20colluding%20with%20government%20officials%2C%20took%20possession%20of%20lands%20illegally%20by%20fudging%20the%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPerhaps%20KCR%20thought%20his%20dominance%20was%20set%20in%20stone%20because%2C%20over%20two%20terms%2C%20he%20had%20practically%20decimated%20the%20political%20opposition%20and%20throttled%20civil%20society.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDominance%20means%20destroying%20the%20opposition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20political%20arena%2C%20the%20first%20target%20was%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP)%2C%20of%20which%20he%20was%20a%20member%20before%20the%20BRS%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20previous%20avatar%20of%20TRS%20%E2%80%93%20was%20founded.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202016%2C%20two%20years%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%2012%20of%2015%20TDP%20MLAs%20defected%20to%20the%20TRS.%20In%20subsequent%20years%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20influence%20waned%20in%20Telangana%20and%20it%20decided%20not%20to%20contest%20the%20recently%20concluded%20polls%20because%20of%20the%20legal%20troubles%20that%20TDP%20supremo%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20facing%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20he%20turned%20his%20attention%20towards%20the%20Congress%2C%20a%20party%20that%20could%20claim%20credit%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20Telangana%2C%20which%20KCR%20had%20promised%20to%20merge%20with%20in%202014%20before%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fsouth%2Fstory%2Ftrs-says-no-merger-with-congress-183545-2014-03-03%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereneging%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Just%20six%20months%20after%20the%20elections%20in%20December%202018%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20Congress%20MLAs%20defected%20to%20join%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20first%20term%2C%20the%20defection%20of%20TDP%20MLAs%20helped%20shore%20up%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20numbers.%20The%20party%20won%2063%20seats%2C%20just%20over%20the%20majority%20mark%20of%2060.%20But%20even%20after%20winning%20a%20brute%20majority%20of%2088%20seats%20in%20the%20second%20term%2C%20KCR%20continued%20to%20dismantle%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weakening%20of%20these%20two%20parties%20allowed%20the%20BJP%20to%20fill%20the%20vacuum.%20It%20consistently%20performed%20well%20in%20by-polls%2C%20increasing%20its%20tally%20and%20expanding%20its%20footprint%20under%20dynamic%20leader%20Bandi%20Sanjay.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20posed%20KCR%20a%20problem%3A%20backed%20by%20money%20power%20and%20the%20might%20of%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20prove%20to%20be%20a%20much%20tougher%20opponent%20than%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20Congress%20put%20together.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20saffron%20party%20inexplicably%20faded%20away%20in%20the%20past%20six%20months%20as%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20resurrected.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29151251%2FBJP-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29151251%2FBJP-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29151251%2FBJP-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F29151251%2FBJP.jpeg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686919%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22630%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Telangana%20BJP%20under%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20(third%20from%20right)%20was%20the%20primary%20opposition%20party%20in%20the%20state%20until%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40BJP4Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20comeback%20vs%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20hubris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJust%20as%20the%20Congress%20came%20back%20from%20the%20dead%2C%20the%20suppressed%20voices%20of%20intellectuals%20and%20civil%20society%20became%20louder%20as%20the%20elections%20approached.%20Even%20those%20who%20had%20supported%20KCR%20in%20the%20past%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D1056%26v%3DUMuLDfXQeOM%26embeds_referring_euri%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%2F%26embeds_referring_origin%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.newslaundry.com%26source_ve_path%3DMjM4NTE%26feature%3Demb_title%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enow%20became%20staunch%20critics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Those%20who%20stuck%20their%20neck%20out%20knew%20they%20would%20pay%20a%20great%20cost%20if%20the%20BRS%20retained%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20in%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20own%20hubris%20that%20led%20to%20his%20downfall.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20opinion%20polls%20put%20the%20Congress%20ahead%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20KCR%20was%20still%20a%20favourable%20choice%20for%20chief%20minister%20among%20the%20people.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EHad%20he%20taken%20the%20legitimate%20grievances%20of%20the%20people%20seriously%2C%20been%20more%20available%20and%20done%20more%20to%20fill%20vacancies%20in%20government%20jobs%2C%20a%20hattrick%20could%20have%20been%20conceivable.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESensing%20the%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%2C%20had%20he%20fielded%20new%20candidates%2C%20the%20results%20may%20have%20been%20starkly%20different.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20such%20is%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20arrogance%20that%20he%20once%20claimed%20even%20if%20he%20fields%20a%20dog%20as%20a%20candidate%2C%20people%20will%20vote%20for%20that%20dog.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20patriarch%20of%20Telangana%2C%20as%20he%20perhaps%20sees%20himself%2C%20will%20not%20just%20fade%20away%20into%20the%20shadows.%20It%20is%20clear%20that%20he%20will%20resurrect%20himself%20and%20his%20party.%20If%20he%20gets%20another%20shot%20at%20power%2C%20KCR%20will%20do%20well%20to%20remember%20that%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20people%20did%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20hold%20their%20elected%20representatives%20accountable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20days%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Edora%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Es%20(feudal%20lords)%20have%20long%20gone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701871850000%2C%2