nes-13024067%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fjoseph-emerson-attempted-murder-charges-dropped-against-pilot-who-tried-to-cut-engines-13024067%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Apple%20reworked%20its%20strategy%20for%20iPhones%20made%20in%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701862990000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105785669%2Cimgsize-36316.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-indias-national-security-concerns-has-made-apple-rework-its-strategy-for-iphones-made-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F105785529.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20seeking%20new%20suppliers%2C%20including%20Indian%2C%20Japanese%2C%20and%20South%20Korean%20component%20makers%2C%20due%20to%20delayed%20government%20clearances%20for%20imports%20from%20existing%20Chinese%20suppliers.%20The%20company%20aims%20to%20establish%20%26quot%3Bjust-in-time%26quot%3B%20supply%20chains%20in%20India%20to%20expedite%20local%20production%20of%20flagship%20iPhones%20and%20iPads.%20While%2014%20Chinese%20companies%20received%20initial%20approvals%20to%20set%20up%20manufacturing%20facilities%20in%20India%2C%20the%20applications%20of%20four%20companies%20have%20been%20indefinitely%20delayed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-indias-national-security-concerns-has-made-apple-rework-its-strategy-for-iphones-made-in-india%2Farticleshow%2F105785529.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22B.R.%20Ambedkar's%20Fears%20on%20the%20EC's%20Independence%2C%20Boycott%20of%20Minorities%20Are%20Coming%20True%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECoincidentally%2C%20India%20is%20observing%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20solemn%20Maha%20Parinirvan%20Day%20of%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20on%20December%206%2C%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20election%20results%20for%20state%20assemblies%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Mizoram%20were%20declared%20and%20the%20impartiality%20and%20fairness%20of%20the%20Election%20Commission%20(EC)%20in%20conducting%20elections%20was%20questioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventy-seven%20years%20after%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20passing%20away%2C%20his%20apprehensions%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20provision%20in%20the%20Constitution%20preventing%20the%20executive%20to%20appoint%20a%20foolish%2C%20knave%20or%20a%20pliable%20person%20as%20election%20commissioner%20or%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20%E2%80%93%20making%20the%20EC%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20have%20come%20true.%20He%20said%20so%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20June%2016%2C%201949%2C%20during%20the%20debates%20on%20the%20draft%20Article%20289%20(now%20Article%20324)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20dealing%20with%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20not%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20EC%20in%20the%20conduct%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20aforementioned%20state%20assemblies%20testified%20to%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20Ambedkar%20that%20it%20would%20come%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20was%20in%20operation%20and%20election%20campaign%20was%20at%20its%20peak%2C%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20prevent%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20when%20it%20released%20money%20to%20the%20people%20under%20the%20Ladli%20Behena%20scheme.%20In%20contrast%20it%20prevented%20the%20Telangana%20government%20from%20releasing%20money%20to%20farmers%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20Scheme.%20It%20clearly%20proved%20the%20point%20that%20the%20standard%20employed%20by%20the%20EC%20for%20BJP%20state%20governments%20was%20not%20applied%20to%20the%20Telangana%20government.%20The%20glaring%20differentiation%20in%20applying%20one%20norm%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20in%20MP%20and%20the%20non-application%20of%20the%20same%20norm%20for%20Telangana%20is%20evocative%20of%20the%20doctrine%20of%20differential%20rights%20often%20employed%20by%20the%20colonial%20rulers%20in%20India%20to%20discriminate%20against%20Indians%20and%20favour%20the%20whites%20who%20wielded%20power.%20It%20is%20tragic%20that%20the%20same%20doctrine%20is%20in%20operation%20in%20the%20action%20of%20EC%2C%20which%20in%20the%20words%20of%20Ambedkar%20has%20%E2%80%9Ccome%20under%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%20resonated%20in%20Supreme%20Court%20judgement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehension%20expressed%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20in%201949%20was%20also%20reflected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20which%20in%20its%20judgement%20of%20March%202%2C%202023%20prescribed%20a%20group%20consisting%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20chief%20justice%20of%20India%20and%20leader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20to%20select%20members%20of%20EC%20so%20that%20it%20is%20not%20reduced%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cservile%20commission%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20Ambedkar%20while%20moving%20the%20draft%20Article%20289%20in%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20on%20June%2015%2C%201949%20for%20setting%20up%20an%20Election%20Commission%2C%20had%20said%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%5BW%5Dithout%20any%20kind%20of%20dissent%2C%20that%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20purity%20and%20freedom%20of%20elections%20to%20the%20legislative%20bodies%2C%20it%20was%20of%20utmost%20importance%20that%20they%20should%20be%20freed%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20interference%20from%20the%20executive%20of%20the%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20EC%20only%20issued%20notices%20to%20some%20opposition%20leaders%20on%20the%20charge%20that%20they%20violated%20the%20MCC%20and%20completely%20ignored%20the%20complaints%20of%20opposition%20parties%20against%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20for%20invoking%20religion%20for%20seeking%20votes%20clearly%20proved%20the%20point%20that%20the%20EC%20did%20not%20act%20impartially.%20It%20is%20in%20such%20tragic%20circumstances%20that%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20cautionary%20words%20assume%20critical%20significance%20for%20summoning%20the%20collective%20energy%20for%20addressing%20the%20problem%20caused%20by%20the%20EC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20intervention%20of%20the%20courts%2C%20in%20particular%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20in%20this%20regard%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance.%20The%20Modi%20government%20has%20prepared%20a%20Bill%20overturning%20the%20aforementioned%20order%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20by%20replacing%20the%20CJI%20in%20the%20collegium-like%20committee%20to%20select%20members%20of%20the%20EC%20with%20a%20nominee%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20It%20means%20that%20it%20wants%20to%20play%20out%20the%20apprehensions%20of%20Ambedkar%20that%20the%20EC%20would%20come%20%E2%80%9Cunder%20the%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbedkar%E2%80%99s%20apprehensions%20on%20boycott%20of%20minorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20solemn%20occasion%20of%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20death%20anniversary%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20to%20see%20in%20retrospect%20his%20draft%20Constitution%20for%20the%20United%20States%20of%20India.%20He%20prepared%20it%20in%201945%20and%20submitted%20it%20to%20a%20sub-committee%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly.%20Anticipating%20that%20minorities%20in%20India%20would%20be%20boycotted%20in%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20realms%20on%20account%20of%20the%20discrimination%20meted%20out%20to%20them%20because%20of%20their%20faith%2C%20he%20dealt%20with%20the%20issue%20very%20elaborately%20and%20provided%20a%20separate%20section%20under%20the%20captions%20%E2%80%9CProvisions%20for%20the%20protection%20of%20minorities%E2%80%9D%2C%20%E2%80%9Cprotection%20against%20social%20boycott.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20defined%20boycott%20in%20very%20broad%20terms%2C%20which%20is%20applicable%20for%20our%20times%20marked%20by%20calls%20issued%20by%20several%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20many%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Edharma%20sansads%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%98%20or%20Religious%20Parliaments%20for%20boycott%20of%20Muslims%20so%20that%20their%20exclusion%20from%20social%20and%20economic%20fields%20are%20ensured.%20He%20also%20dealt%20with%20measures%20which%20would%20amount%20to%20instigation%20and%20promotion%20of%20boycott%20and%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhoever%20publicly%20makes%20or%20publishes%20or%20circulates%20a%20proposal%20for%20or%20makes%2C%20publishes%20or%20circulates%20any%20statement%2C%20rumour%20or%20report%20with%20intent%20to%2C%20or%20which%20he%20has%20reason%20to%20believe%20to%20be%20likely%20to%20cause%2C%20or%20in%20any%20other%20way%20instigates%20or%20promotes%20the%20boycotting%20of%20any%20person%20or%20class%20of%20persons%2C%20shall%20be%20guilty%20of%20the%20offence%20of%20instigating%20or%20promoting%20a%20boycott.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20farsighted%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20offences%20shall%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20cognisable%20offences%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Union%20legislature%20shall%20make%20laws%20prescribing%20punishment%20for%20these%20offences%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETragically%20inside%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20a%20constituent%20of%20the%20Union%20legislature%2C%20a%20BJP%20member%2C%20hurled%20abuses%20against%20another%20MP%20on%20account%20of%20his%20faith%20and%20no%20penal%20action%20has%20so%20far%20been%20taken%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20provided%20by%20Ambedkar%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20existential%20crises%20confronting%20our%20republic%20are%20of%20critical%20significance%20for%2021st-century%20India.%20Remaining%20sensitive%20to%20his%20concerns%20and%20taking%20remedial%20action%20for%20safeguarding%20the%20Constitution%20would%20constitute%20true%20tribute%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20Sahu%20served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%20India%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701861645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F14124741%2FIMG_1874-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fb-r-ambedkars-fears-on-the-ecs-independence-boycott-of-minorities-are-coming-true%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Election%20Commission's%20actions%20during%20the%20recent%20state%20assembly%20elections%20suggest%20that%20Ambedkar's%20warning%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20may%20come%20under%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20thumb%20of%20the%20executive%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20was%20well%20placed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fb-r-ambedkars-fears-on-the-ecs-independence-boycott-of-minorities-are-coming-true%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20financier%20extradited%20to%20Denmark%20over%20%241.7bn%20tax%20fraud%20charges%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701861300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-sanjay-shah-elysium_6384000.jpg%3F20231206112300%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-financier-sanjay-shah-facing-charges-over-17bn-fraud-extradited-to-denmark-from-uae-13024051%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Dubai-based%20British%20hedge%20fund%20trader%20accused%20of%20orchestrating%20a%20%241.7bn%20(%C2%A31.34bn)%20tax%20fraud%20has%20been%20extradited%20to%20Denmark.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A56%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-financier-sanjay-shah-facing-charges-over-1-7bn-fraud-extradited-to-denmark-from-uae-13024051%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-financier-sanjay-shah-facing-charges-over-1-7bn-fraud-extradited-to-denmark-from-uae-13024051%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fbritish-financier-sanjay-shah-facing-charges-over-1-7bn-fraud-extradited-to-denmark-from-uae-13024051%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran%20sends%20space%20capsule%20carrying%20animals%20into%20orbit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701860100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F12%2F768x432%2Fskynews-iran-rocket_6383864.jpg%3F20231206092532%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Firan-sends-space-capsule-carrying-animals-into-orbit-13024029%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iran%20said%20it%20has%20launched%20a%20capsule%20into%20space%20carrying%20animals%20as%20it%20prepares%20to%20send%20up%20astronauts%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A88%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Firan-sends-space-capsule-carrying-animals-into-orbit-13024029%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Firan-sends-space-capsule-carrying-animals-into-orbit-13024029%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Firan-sends-space-capsule-carrying-animals-into-orbit-13024029%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%20Evading%20Accountability%2C%20Indian%20Military%20Suffers%20More%20Losses%20Than%20Those%20Inflicted%20by%20Enemies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06155517%2FEffect-14-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20military%20is%20frequently%20hailed%20as%20the%20last%20defence%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20more%20than%20just%20the%20defender%20of%20the%20territory%3B%20it%20is%20the%20protector%20of%20the%20constitution%20itself.%20As%20for%20its%20size%2C%20the%20ministry%20of%20defence%20gets%20about%2013.18%20%25%20of%20the%20total%20budget%2C%20catering%20to%20about%201.4%20million%20active%20personnel.%20Given%20such%20importance%2C%20it%20is%20only%20natural%20that%20it%20is%20made%20accountable%20to%20the%20people%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findia-suffered-1874-casualties-without-fighting-a-war%2Farticleshow%2F45016284.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202003%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20life%20of%20an%20Indian%20army%20soldier%20comes%20cheap.%20The%20US-led%20coalition%20forces%20lost%20just%20around%20150%20personnel%20during%20the%20Iraq%20operations%2C%20but%20almost%202%2C000%20Indian%20army%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20or%20wounded%20during%20the%2010-month%20forward%20deployment%20along%20the%20Indo-Pak%20border%20last%20year.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20else%20do%20you%20expect%3F%20We%20have%20to%20soldier%20on%2C%20even%20without%20basic%20necessities%20like%20decent%20helmets%2C%20proper%20webbing%20or%20bulletproof%20jackets%2C%E2%80%9D%20retorted%20an%20angry%20young%20major.%20In%202016%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia%2Fof-1-000-soldiers-lost-in-siachen-only-220-fell-to-enemy-bullets%2Fstory-FLvSUFDAnnmUt5oiagQ8hK.html%5C%22%3Ereported%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9COf%201%2C000%20soldiers%20lost%20in%20Siachen%2C%20only%20220%20fell%20to%20enemy%20bullets.%E2%80%9D%20In%202017%2C%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F1600-personnel-die-every-year-without-india-going-to-war%2Farticleshow%2F61898366.cms%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20accidents%2C%20suicides%2C%20and%20ailments%20kill%20about%201%2C600%20soldiers%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurely%2C%20something%20is%20amiss.%20What%20is%20missing%20is%20accountability%2C%20buttressed%20with%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20present%20system%20allows%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%20to%20have%20layers%20of%20opaqueness%20that%20completely%20kill%20any%20notion%20of%20transparency.%20A%20right%20to%20information%20(RTI)%20application%20once%20sought%20the%20broad%20distribution%20of%20periods%20among%20the%20main%20areas%20of%20training%20provided%20by%20the%20National%20Defence%20Academy%20(NDA).%20The%20particular%20three-year%20training%20is%20the%20basic%20training%20provided%20by%20the%20Indian%20armed%20forces%2C%20which%20is%20also%20attended%20by%20cadets%20from%20numerous%20foreign%20countries.%20The%20RTI%20applicant%20wanted%20data%20to%20support%20his%20claim%20that%20despite%20the%20claim%20of%20NDA%20being%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccradle%20of%20leadership%E2%80%9D%2C%20it%20simply%20does%20not%20%E2%80%98train%E2%80%99%20cadets%20for%20leadership.%20The%20application%20was%20refused%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20national%20security.%20When%20probed%20for%20an%20explanation%2C%20it%20was%20offered%20that%20disclosing%20the%20topics%20would%20lay%20bare%20the%20operational%20concepts%20of%20Indian%20armed%20forces!%20Of%20course%2C%20this%20is%20pure%20humbug.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20transparency%20in%20Indian%20institutions%20has%20always%20been%20an%20uphill%20task.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frsf.org%2Fen%2Findex%5C%22%3E2023%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20Index%2C%20by%20Reporters%20without%20Borders%2C%20shows%20India%E2%80%99s%20slide%20from%20150th%20position%20in%202022%20to%20161%20in%202023.%20Yes%2C%20161%20out%20of%20just%20180%20counties%2C%20a%20slide%20of%2011%20positions%20in%20just%20one%20year!%20In%20the%20same%20period%2C%20Pakistan%20improved%20its%20standing%20from%20157%20to%20150th%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fexclusive-army-officer-wilfully-suppressed-info-that-could-have-prevented-nagaland-killings-says-sit%5C%22%3EExclusive%3A%20Army%20Officer%20%E2%80%98Wilfully%20Suppressed%E2%80%99%20Info%20That%20Could%20Have%20Prevented%20Nagaland%20Killings%2C%20Says%20SIT%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20defence%20ministry%20has%C2%A0already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fnagaland-civilian-killings-afspa-prosecution%5C%22%3Edenied%20sanction%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20prosecute%20Indian%20Army%20officers%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%20in%20Nagaland%E2%80%99s%20Oting%20in%20December%202021.%20The%20army%20accepts%20that%20its%20personnel%20killed%20six%20unarmed%20civilians%2C%20but%20says%20they%20did%20so%20%E2%80%9Cas%20a%20case%20of%20mistaken%20identity%E2%80%9D.%20That%E2%80%99s%20only%20one%20side%20of%20the%20story.%20Whether%20it%20was%20punishable%20or%20not%20can%20only%20be%20determined%20by%20law%2C%20but%20the%20government%20protects%20the%20killers%20from%20facing%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20seeking%20transparency%20be%20easy%20in%20such%20a%20climate%3F%20Equally%2C%20is%20anything%20more%20important%20than%20striving%20for%20it%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20culture%20of%20impunity%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccountability%20is%20not%20a%20matter%20of%20just%20rules%20and%20regulations.%20Attempts%20at%20transparency%20are%20resisted%20less%20by%20the%20government%20and%20more%20by%20the%20mindset%20of%20citizens%20themselves.%20The%20reigning%20mindset%20is%20that%20%E2%80%98our%20boys%20are%20doing%20all%20they%20can%20in%20difficult%20circumstances%2C%20hence%20they%20ought%20to%20be%20thanked%20for%20what%20they%20manage%20to%20achieve%2C%20rather%20than%20be%20questioned%20for%20what%20they%20could%20not%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20right%20mindset%2C%20however%2C%20should%20be%20that%20while%20they%20indeed%20must%20be%20thanked%20for%20what%20they%20achieve%2C%20they%20must%20also%20be%20held%20accountable%20for%20their%20lapses.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20those%20who%20create%20the%20problems%20in%20the%20first%20place%20and%20those%20who%20pull%20the%20chestnuts%20out%20of%20the%20fire%20later%20are%20not%20the%20same%20groups%20of%20people.%20In%20our%20desire%20to%20focus%20only%20on%20the%20second%20group%2C%20the%20first%20group%20manages%20to%20slip%20away%20from%20public%20scrutiny.%20They%20just%20live%20to%20cause%20more%20damage%20yet%20another%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20contemporary%20example%20of%20the%20labourers%20trapped%20in%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20While%20we%20must%20applaud%20the%20efforts%20to%20rescue%20them%2C%20the%20organisers%20must%20be%20made%20to%20answer%20how%20they%20went%20ahead%20with%20the%20tunneling%20work%20without%20taking%20even%20the%20most%20basic%20precautions.%20One%20NGO%20has%20rightly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.rediff.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Freport%2Fngo-files-pil-on-silkyara-tunnel-rescue-hc-seeks-govt-reply-in-48-hrs%2F20231120.htm%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20PIL%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alleging%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20construction%20of%20the%20tunnel%2C%20geological%20investigation%20of%20the%20area%20was%20not%20done%20properly%20and%20norms%20of%20digging%20a%20tunnel%20were%20not%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221092%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx.jpeg%201092w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01140335%2FGACaXNpbYAASMBx-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687236%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22819%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERescuers%20at%20the%20mouth%20of%20the%20Silkyara%20tunnel.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40KirenRijiju%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20there%20have%20been%20numerous%20instances%20of%20this%20type.%20The%20Sikkim%20Chungthang%20dam%20disaster%20was%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fopinion%2Fsikkim-flood-teesta-dam-breach-told-you-so-moment-hydropower-history%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20told%20you%20so%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20moment.%20Everyone%20knew%20what%20was%20happening.%20Do%20you%20even%20remember%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fjoshimath-sinking-how-man-made-factors-assaulted-fragile-ecology-101673290161100.html%5C%22%3Esinking%20Joshimath%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Even%20after%20so%20many%20incidents%2C%20no%20heads%20have%20rolled.%20They%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOperational%20inefficiency%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20is%20the%20army%20faring%20in%20all%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficers%20constitute%20just%204%25%20of%20the%20army.%20However%2C%20their%20casualty%20rate%20in%20anti-terrorist%20actions%20is%20disproportionately%20higher%2C%20more%20than%2010%25.%20While%20we%20must%20commend%20our%20officers%20for%20their%20bravery%2C%20it%20mustn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20us%20from%20also%20questioning%20why%20so%20many%20officers%2C%20trained%20for%20years%20in%20expensive%20institutions%2C%20fall%20prey%20so%20easily%20to%20teams%20of%201-3%20terrorists.%20These%20terrorists%20are%20ill-trained%2C%20hold%20rusty%20equipment%2C%20and%20are%20surrounded%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%20on%20all%20sides.%20Further%2C%20these%20casualties%20are%20taking%20place%20not%20in%20terrorist-led%20ambushes%20or%20chance%20encounters%2C%20but%20in%20intelligence-led%20deliberate%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06160051%2FEffect-15.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06160051%2FEffect-15.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06160051%2FEffect-15-300x140.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06160051%2FEffect-15-1024x478.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687960%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIndian%20army%20soldier.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FNorthern%20Command-Indian%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20level%20of%20fighting%20efficiency%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjammu-kashmir-militant-rajouri-encounter-four-soldiers-army-killed%5C%22%3Etwo%20recent%20incidents%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20quite%20revealing.%20In%20the%20Rajouri%20incident%2C%20two%20officers%20were%20killed.%20In%20the%20Kokernag%20incident%2C%20a%20commanding%20officer%2C%20a%20major%20and%20a%20police%20officer%20were%20killed.%20Both%20incidents%20were%20deliberate%20operations%20launched%20after%20definite%20intelligence.%20The%20Kokernag%20incident%20also%20saw%20militarily%20unacceptable%20behaviour%20by%20troops%20in%20contact.%20They%20broke%20contact%20and%20did%20not%20evacuate%20the%20injured%20police%20officer%20for%20hours%2C%20who%20finally%20died%20of%20excessive%20bleeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20look%20at%20any%20television%20debate%20after%20such%20incidents%20invariably%20shows%20army%20generals%20loudly%20thanking%20the%20deceased%20officers%20%E2%80%98who%20led%20from%20the%20front%E2%80%99.%20The%20generals%20conveniently%20forget%20that%20officers%20leading%20search%20parties%20are%20not%20the%20way%20it%20is%20taught%20in%20army%20training%20institutions.%20These%20operations%20are%20to%20to%20be%20led%20by%20soldier%20scouts%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20bunch%20of%20other%20soldiers%20led%20by%20Havildars%20and%20Junior%20Commissioned%20Officers%20(JCOs).%20If%20a%20Commanding%20Officer%2C%20or%20other%20officer%2C%20is%20forced%20to%20overrule%20this%20technique%20and%20himself%20lead%20strike%20elements%2C%20prima%20facie%20it%20appears%20that%20he%20realises%20that%20the%20scouts%2C%20Havildars%20and%20JCOs%20are%20unfit%20for%20their%20jobs.%20If%20the%20reason%20is%20something%20else%2C%20the%20army%20must%20be%20forced%20to%20provide%20that%20reason.%20When%20martyrdom%20becomes%20more%20important%20than%20skill%2C%20one%20remembers%20General%20Patton%20who%20once%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20bast**d%20ever%20won%20a%20war%20by%20dying%20for%20his%20country.%20He%20won%20it%20by%20making%20the%20other%20poor%20dumb%20bast**d%20die%20for%20his%20country.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpulwama-attack-kin-of-slain-jawans-demand-answers-from-centre-to-hold-protest-march-in-delhi%5C%22%3EPulwama%20Attack%3A%20Kin%20of%20Slain%20Jawans%20Demand%20Answers%20from%20Centre%2C%20to%20Hold%20Protest%20March%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20television%20debates%2C%20most%20generals%20offer%20a%20line%20that%20the%20army%20learns%20from%20all%20events.%20Is%20it%20so%3F%20If%20it%20were%2C%20the%20number%20of%20officers%20and%20jawans%20being%20killed%20would%20have%20declined%2C%20not%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20Training%20Command%20has%20a%20centre%20for%20learning%20lessons%20called%20CALL%20(Center%20for%20Army%20Lessons%20Learnt).%20In%202022%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20to%20an%20RTI%20applicant%20that%20CALL%20had%20not%20produced%20any%20output%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20due%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20Surprisingly%2C%202020-20222%20was%20the%20period%20in%20which%20the%20Indian%20army%20was%20involved%20in%20several%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20militants%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Chinese%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20any%20case%2C%20enforcing%20accountability%20is%20not%20a%20dictum%20that%20every%20military%20person%20questioned%20by%20responsible%20citizens%20must%20be%20punished.%20All%20it%20means%20is%20that%20if%20things%20went%20horribly%20wrong%2C%20they%20must%20provide%20an%20explanation%20for%20what%20they%20did%20%E2%80%93%20or%20did%20not%20do.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20fair%20that%20those%20who%20fund%20the%20military%20be%20allowed%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20how%20their%20money%20is%20utilised%2C%20and%20how%20their%20children%20go%20to%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20deterrence%20worked%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHas%20the%20non-transparency%20helped%20the%20army%20be%20more%20effective%3F%20What%20has%20been%20the%20demonstrated%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20Indian%20army%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%201947%20till%202023%2C%20India%20used%20its%20armed%20forces%20very%20frequently.%20In%201948-49%2C%20Pakistan%20intruded%20into%20India.%20In%201962%2C%20the%20Chinese%20did.%20In%201965%2C%20Pakistanis%20again%20intruded.%20They%20did%20so%20again%20in%20Kargil%20in%201999.%20China%2C%20too%2C%20has%20steadily%20encroached%20on%20Indian%20territory%20from%20the%2060s%20till%20now%2C%20i.e.%2C%202023.%20This%20shows%20that%20deterrence%20of%20the%20Indian%20military%20has%20never%20worked.%20No%20adversary%20takes%20the%20Indian%20military%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20502px)%2085vw%2C%20502px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F20172611%2FKargil_war.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22502%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F20172611%2FKargil_war.jpg%20375w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F12%2F20172611%2FKargil_war-300x276.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323067%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EKargil%20war.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20this%20century.%20After%20the%20Indian%20strike%20at%20Balakot%2C%20it%20was%20expected%20that%20Pakistan%20would%20get%20the%20message%20of%20Indian%20military%20might%20and%20would%20be%20deterred.%20But%20it%20chose%20not%20to.%20The%20very%20next%20day%2C%20it%20attacked%20the%20Indian%20mainland%2C%20using%20its%20Air%20Force%2C%20in%20broad%20daylight%2C%20on%20February%2027%2C%202019.%20Against%20that%20act%20of%20war%2C%20it%20was%20India%20that%20chose%20to%20do%20nothing%20about%20it.%20India%20did%20not%20attack%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20our%20only%20achievement%20is%20that%20we%20have%20not%20lost%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20satisfactory%20outcome%20for%20the%20money%20spent%20and%20sacrifices%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20armed%20forces%20have%20never%20faced%20tough%20questions%20about%20its%20performance.%20Enquiries%2C%20even%20when%20held%2C%20fail%20to%20hold%20the%20guilty%20accountable.%20The%20debacle%20of%20the%201962%20was%20indeed%20investigated%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FHenderson_Brooks%25E2%2580%2593Bhagat_Report%5C%22%3EHenderson%20Brooks-Bhagat%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20but%20the%20nation%20has%20still%20not%20been%20shown%20that%20report%2C%20in%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20interest%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Kargil%20War%20debacle%20was%20never%20investigated.%20Yes%2C%20seen%20from%20the%20defence%20perspective%2C%20it%20was%20a%20major%20debacle.%20The%20fact%20that%20India%20managed%20to%20win%20back%20the%20lost%20territory%20is%20not%20as%20relevant%20as%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20large%20tracts%20of%20critical%20importance%20were%20conveniently%20lost%20to%20a%20known%20enemy%2C%20without%20as%20much%20as%20one%20bullet%20being%20fired.%20That%E2%80%99s%20plain%20inefficiency.%20Unlike%20the%201962%20war%2C%20this%20debacle%20was%20not%20even%20subjected%20to%20an%20enquiry.%20A%20committee%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FKargil_Review_Committee%5C%22%3EKargil%20Review%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E)%20was%20indeed%20constituted%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20to%20study%20why%20and%20how%20the%20intrusion%20was%20allowed%20to%20happen.%20It%20was%20merely%20to%20%E2%80%9Cexamine%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%20and%20make%20recommendations%20for%20the%20future%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmies%20do%20a%20difficult%20job%20in%20war.%20Combat%20requires%20actions%20to%20be%20initiated%20which%20have%20a%20low%20chance%20of%20success%20but%20must%20be%20taken%20anyway.%20It%20is%20legitimate%20to%20fear%20that%20in%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20the%20looming%20threat%20of%20public%20enquiry%20might%20over-deter%20the%20decision%20makers.%20Here%20we%20must%20differentiate%20between%20decisions%20taken%20during%20actual%20combat%20and%20those%20taken%20in%20the%20intervening%20years%20of%20peace%20when%20armies%20are%20systematically%20trained%20and%20equipped%20for%20those%20short%20periods%20of%20actual%20combat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%98Combat%20immunity%E2%80%99%20and%20due%20care%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-22967853%5C%22%3EA%20case%20came%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20UK%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20three%20cases%20clubbed%20into%20one.%20In%20case%20one%2C%20some%20soldiers%20in%20a%20tank%20died%20because%20of%20some%20other%20soldiers%20of%20the%20same%20force%20firing%20on%20them%2C%20mistaking%20them%20to%20be%20the%20enemy.%20In%20cases%20two%20and%20three%2C%20soldiers%20died%20in%20two%20separate%20incidents%20of%20IED%20blasts%20damaging%20their%20Land%20Rover%20vehicles.%20In%20these%20three%20cases%2C%20families%20of%20the%20soldiers%20filed%20for%20compensation%20from%20the%20employer%20of%20the%20soldiers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20ministry%20of%20defence.%20In%20case%20one%2C%20the%20appellant%20claimed%20that%20the%20tank%20used%20by%20the%20deceased%20lacked%20features%20that%20could%20have%20prevented%20the%20incident%20altogether.%20The%20deaths%20directly%20resulted%20from%20the%20soldiers%20not%20having%20been%20provided%20with%20adequate%20recognition%20and%20situational%20awareness%20training%2C%20which%20would%20have%20helped%20avoid%20the%20friendly%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20claim%20in%20cases%20two%20and%20three%20was%20that%20deaths%20were%20a%20result%20of%20using%20the%20wrong%20instrument%20for%20the%20task.%20The%20Land%20Rover%20vehicle%20did%20not%20have%20adequate%20protection%20against%20the%20known%20dangers%20of%20that%20area.%20It%20was%20argued%20that%20a%20more%20potent%20vehicle%2C%20suitable%20for%20the%20area%2C%20should%20have%20been%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-soldiers-deaths-accountable%5C%22%3EShould%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20Be%20Sued%20for%20the%20Deaths%20of%20Soldiers%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UK%20MoD%20pleaded%20%E2%80%98combat%20immunity%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20that%20it%20should%20be%20given%20a%20sufficiently%20broad%20scope%20to%20cover%20all%20acts%20or%20omissions%20alleged%20to%20have%20caused%20death%20or%20injury%20during%20combat%20operations.%20It%20also%20pleaded%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20fair%2C%20just%2C%20or%20reasonable%20to%20impose%20a%20duty%20of%20care%20on%20the%20M0D%20in%20the%20circumstances%20of%20those%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdefence-ministry-soldiers-deaths-accountable%5C%22%3Eruled%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20army%20indeed%20has%20the%20right%20to%20decide%20what%20equipment%20they%20want%20to%20use%20in%20combat.%20Thus%2C%20the%20doctrine%20of%20combat%20immunity%20was%20upheld.%20However%2C%20the%20court%20went%20on%20to%20clarify%20that%20the%20doctrine%20should%20be%20construed%20narrowly%20and%20not%20extended%20beyond%20its%20established%20scope%20of%20actual%20combat%20operations%2C%20to%20the%20planning%20of%20and%20preparation%20for%20active%20operations%20against%20the%20enemy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20combat%20immunity%20is%20only%20for%20actual%20combat%20and%20does%20not%20hold%20for%20decisions%20which%20are%20taken%20far%20removed%20from%20the%20pressures%20and%20risks%20of%20active%20operations%20against%20the%20enemy.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20admissibility%20of%20the%20claim%20of%20negligence%2C%20or%20death%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20proper%20training%20and%20protection%20measures%20in%20equipment%20used%2C%20was%20tentatively%20upheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20employers%20have%20a%20responsibility%20of%20due%20care%20over%20their%20employees.%20When%20a%20civilian%20contractor%20sends%20a%20construction%20worker%20to%20work%20on%20a%20scaffolding%2C%20it%20is%20mandated%20by%20law%20that%20he%20provides%20a%20helmet%2C%20a%20harness%2C%20and%20training%20on%20how%20to%20work%20safely%20while%20on%20a%20scaffolding.%20If%20the%20employer%20fails%20to%20do%20so%2C%20he%20is%20liable%20for%20any%20ill%20effects%20of%20his%20lapse.%20He%20has%20the%20obligation%20of%20%E2%80%98due%20care%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pressure%20of%20due%20care%20can%20be%20made%20to%20work%20in%20two%20ways%20%E2%80%93%20reactively%20and%20proactively.%20The%20reactive%20part%20of%20pressure%20comes%20into%20play%20as%20the%20liability%20to%20compensate.%20But%20must%20we%20wait%20till%20some%20damage%20occurs%2C%20or%20is%20it%20better%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20avoid%20the%20chances%20of%20such%20errors%3F%20For%20this%20preventive%20action%20to%20even%20start%2C%20a%20close%20watch%20must%20be%20maintained%20on%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20system.%20This%20is%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98due%20diligence%E2%80%99%2C%20made%20possible%20only%20by%20transparency.%20It%20maintains%20positive%20and%20constructive%20pressure%20on%20employers%20to%20act%20with%20%E2%80%98due%20care%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98due%20diligence%E2%80%99%2C%20so%20that%20harm%20is%20avoided%2C%20rather%20than%20later%20compensated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20citizen%20being%20the%20watchdog%20of%20the%20army%20is%20the%20option%20%E2%80%93%20the%20only%20option%20left.%20It%20can%20be%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20the%20law%20or%20even%20the%20government%20that%20will%20prevent%20setting%20up%20such%20a%20system%20in%20India.%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20LG%20Manoj%20Sinha%20recently%20spoke%20of%20transparent%20and%20accountable%20governance.%20%E2%80%9CPublic%20audit%20ensures%20that%20every%20rupee%20is%20well%20spent%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20bringing%20about%20a%20change%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailyexcelsior.com%2Ftransparent-accountable-governance-by-audit-community-sinha%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Indeed%2C%20every%20rupee%20spent%20on%20defence%2C%20too%2C%20must%20be%20subjected%20to%20public%20audit.%20This%20will%20not%20only%20change%20the%20lives%20of%20soldiers%20but%20also%20spare%20the%20lives%20of%20so%20many%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20already%20brought%20out%2C%20difficulties%20arise%20more%20from%20the%20mindset%20of%20citizens%20themselves.%20They%20will%20see%20it%20as%20an%20unfair%20burden%20on%20an%20army%20which%20is%20up%20against%20such%20heavy%20odds.%20However%2C%20it%20must%20be%20shown%20to%20them%20that%20the%20odds%20against%20the%20army%20come%20not%20only%20from%20the%20adversary%20but%20equally%20from%20the%20system.%20Whatever%20parts%20of%20the%20system%20increase%20those%20odds%20must%20be%20treated%20as%20the%20enemy%20and%20dealt%20with%20equal%20ferocity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guilty%20must%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20escape%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20those%20who%20actually%20sacrifice%20themselves%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Falok-asthana%5C%22%3ECol%20Alok%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EAsthana%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran.%C2%A0He%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Red%20Pill%20on%20India%20and%20Indian%20Army%202023%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHe%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aalok.asthana%40gmail.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealok.%3Cspan%3Easthana%3C%2Fspan%3E%40gmail.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701859791000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F06155517%2FEffect-14-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fby-evading-accountability-indian-military-suffers-more-losses-than-those-inflicted-by-enemies%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22About%201%2C600%20soldiers%20are%20killed%20every%20year%20in%20India%20due%20to%20accidents%2C%20suicides%2C%20and%20ailments.%20It%20is%20the%20prevailing%20mindset%20that%20the%20conduct%20of%20defence%20forces%20can't%20be%20questioned%20results%20in%20such%20avoidable%20circumstances.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fby-evading-accountability-indian-military-suffers-more-losses-than-those-inflicted-by-enemies%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%