2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20pour%20the%20batter%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%3C%2Fem%3Es.%20They%20are%20small%20bowl-shaped%20moulds%20made%20using%20bamboo.%20The%20container%20gives%20the%20batter%20a%20perfect%20idli%20shape.%20We%20then%20place%20these%20small%20bamboo%20bowls%20into%20a%20large%20aluminium%20utensil%20using%20bamboo%20sticks%20for%20support.%20Then%20we%20let%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20slowly%20steam%20over%20firewood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fplugins%2Fpost.php%3Fhref%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.facebook.com%252Fculinaryjourneybynaveen%252Fposts%252Fpfbid0Jhj3eTm6mx67S7cyYDkhocjFkLTESKhrX8GoMGENaQX7v8skATpaV6z67nfotTyxl%26show_text%3Dtrue%26width%3D500%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22689%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVatsala%20informs%20that%20these%20aluminium%20vessels%20%E2%80%94%20around%20two%20feet%20in%20diameter%20%E2%80%94%20have%20the%20capacity%20to%20cook%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eat%20a%20time.%20Every%20day%2C%20Vatsala%20and%20his%20team%20of%20six%20helpers%20prepare%20at%20least%20eight%20batches%20of%2080%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20serve%20their%20now%20ever-growing%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20makes%20these%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Edistinctive%20from%20other%20cooking%20methods%20is%20their%20rich%20aroma%20and%20flavour.%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20prepare%20the%20batter%20in%20the%20same%20manner%20as%20others.%20But%20the%20whole%20process%20of%20cooking%20it%20in%20bamboo%20baskets%20on%20firewood%20imparts%20a%20rustic%20aroma%20and%20flavour%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehave%20attracted%20thousands%20of%20customers%20including%20YouTubers%2C%20Government%20officials%2C%20ministers%2C%20movie%20celebrities%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20popularity%20of%20Babu%20Hotel%20rose%2C%20Vatsala%20says%2C%20several%20other%20restaurants%20have%20cropped%20up%20around%20his%20village%20that%20are%20offering%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20using%20the%20same%20technique.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20attract%20as%20much%20footfall%20as%20we%20do%20because%20the%20making%20of%20these%20%3Cem%3Echiblu%20idlis%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20art.%20Every%20step%20of%20the%20process%20needs%20attention%20to%20detail.%20I%20grew%20up%20watching%20my%20family%20do%20this%2C%20so%20my%20learning%20is%20authentic.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20is%20a%20cumbersome%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20restaurant%20lures%20up%20to%20500%20customers%20on%20any%20weekday.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fidli-1-1700832066-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334923%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20restaurant%20lures%20up%20to%20500%20customers%20on%20any%20weekday.%20Photo%20credit%3A%20Bhakta%20Vatsala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20art%20of%20making%20%3Cem%3Eidlis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20this%20traditional%20man