e%2C%20as%20she%20gave%20the%20viewers%20a%20glimpse%20into%20life%20in%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20strikes%20me%20about%20Nambie%2C%20watching%20her%20videos%2C%20and%20later%2C%20speaking%20to%20her%2C%20is%20her%20simplicity%2C%20authenticity%20and%20realness.%20She%20takes%20her%20viewers%20on%20a%20journey%20to%20Upper%20Rangsa%2C%20showing%20how%20they%20pick%20fresh%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20spices%2C%20and%20cook%20them%20on%20a%20fire%20stove%20outside%20their%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20has%20over%2060%2C000%20followers%20across%20social%20media%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201211px)%20100vw%2C%201211px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221211%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nambie%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top-eight%20finalists%20on%20MasterChef%20India%202023.%5Cn%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473.jpg%201211w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473-263x300.jpg%20263w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473-500x571.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473-768x877.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FNambi2-1700662473-150x171.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-334713%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221383%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENambie%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top-eight%20finalists%20on%20MasterChef%20India%202023.%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20popularity%20of%20her%20channel%20and%20the%20authenticity%20of%20her%20food%20led%20to%20a%20chance%20to%20audition%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2